hadiths[240]{hadithnumber,text}:
5739,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Adam ki aulad ke behtareen tabqaat se hota hua us tabqey mein pahuncha hun jis mein main paida hua hun.'' Bukhari."
5740,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ne aulad Ismail (Alaihissalam) mein se Kinaana ko muntakhab farmaya , Kinaana mein se Quraish ko , Quraish mein se bano Hashim ko aur bano Hashim mein se mujhey muntakhab farmaya.'' aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : ''Allah taala ne Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se Ismail (Alaihissalam) ko muntakhab farmaya , aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se bano kinaana ko.'' rawahu Muslim aur Tirmizi."
5741,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat Adam (Alaihissalam) ki aulad ka sardar main hunga. sab se pehley mujhey qabr se uthaya jaeyga, sab se pehley main sifarish karunga aur sab se pehley meri sifarish qubul ki jaeygi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5742,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat tamam Anbiya (Alaihissalam) se merey muttabein ziyada hongey, aur jannat ke darwazey par sab se pehley main dastak dunga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5743,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat ke din main jannat ke darwazey par aaunga aur uskey kholney ka mutalba karunga to muhafiz puchheyga : aap kon hain? main kahunga : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam). wo arz kerega : aap hi ke mutalliq mujhey hukm diya gaya tha ke aap se pehley kisi ke liye (isey) na kholun.'' rawahu Muslim."
5744,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main jannat mein (dakhley ke liye) sab se pehley sifarish karunga, tamam Anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se meri tasdeeq karney waley ziyada hongey bila shubha Anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se koi aisa Nabi bhi hoga jiski , uski ummat mein sey, sirf eik aadmi ne tasdeeq ki hogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5745,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey aur doosrey Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki misal is tarah hai jaisey eik mehal ho jisey behtareen andaz mein taamir kiya gaya ho, lekin eik eent ki jagah chhod di gaee ho, dekhney waley uskey gird chakkar lagatey hain aur us eent ki jagah ke ilawa uski khubsurat taamir par tajjub mein pad jatey hain, wo main tha jisney us eent ki jagah ko pura kiya. merey sath hi taamir mukammal kar di gaee aur merey sath hi risalat bhi mukammal kar di gaee.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''main hi wo eent hun aur main hi khaatimul-nabiyin hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
5746,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tamam Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ko mojzat ata kiye gaey jinkey mutabiq insan un par eman laye, aur jo mujhey ata kiya gaya wo wahi (yani Quran) hai, Allah ne meri taraf wahi bheji, main ummid karta hun ke roze-qiyamat un (Anbiya (Alaihissalam)) se merey muttabein ziyada hongey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5747,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey paanch chizen ata ki gaee hain, jo mujh se pehley kisi ko ata nahin ki gaeen : eik mahiney ki masafat (doori) se raub ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai, tamam zamin merey liye sajda gaah aur paak bana di gaee hai, merey ummati ko jahan bhi Namaz ka waqt ho jaey to wo wahin Namaz padh ley, merey liye maale-ghanimat halal kar diya gaya hai jabkey mujh se pehley wo kisi ke liye halal nahin tha, mujhey shafaat ata ki gaee hai aur her Nabi apni apni qom ke liye mab-us (bheja) kiya jata tha jabkey mujhey umoomi taur par tamam insanon ke liye mab-us kiya (bheja) gaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5748,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey doosrey Anbiya (Alaihissalam) par chhe chizon se fazilat ata ki gaee hai : mujhey جوامع الکلم  (baat mukhtasar, mafhoom ziyada) ata kiye gaey hain, roab ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai, maale-ghanimat merey liye halal kiya gaya hai, merey liye tamam zamin sajda-gaah aur paak qarar di gaee hai mujhey tamam makhluq ki taraf bheja gaya hai, aur mujh par nabuwat ka silsila khatam kar diya gaya hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5749,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey جوامع الکلم  (baat mukhtasar, mafhoom ziyada) ke sath mab-us kiya (bheja) gaya hai, roab ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai, aur us doran ke main soyaa hua tha maine khuwab mein dekha ke mujhey zamin ke khazanon ki chabiyan ata ki gaee hain, aur unhen merey haath mein rakh diya gaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5750,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne merey liye zamin ko samet diya to maine uskey mashaariq aur magharib ko dekh liya, aur jis qadr zamin merey liye samet di gaee wahan tak meri ummat ki hukumat pahuncheygi, mujhey do khazaney ata kiye gaey, surkh aur safed, maine apney rab se darkhast ki ke wo aam qehat saali (sukhe) ke zariey usey halak na karey, unke bahami (aapsi) dushmanon ke siwa kisi aur dushman ko un par musallat na karey ke wo unka markaz (sadr maqam) tabah kar dey aur bila shubha merey rab ne farmaya : aey Muhammad ! main jab koi faisla kar leta hun to wo tal nahin sakta , maine aap ko aap ki ummat ke barey mein ye ehad dey diya ke main usey qehat saali mein mubtala karkey tabah nahin karunga , ye bhi ehad dey diya ke un par unke bahami (aapsi) dushman ke ilawa koi aisa dushman un par musallat nahin karunga jo unke markaz ko tabah kar dey , agar-che unke tamam dushman muttahid ho kar un par hamla karden, albatta wo aapas main eik doosrey ko halak karengey aur qaidi banaeyngey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5751,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bano Muawiya ki masjid ke paas se guzrey to aap is mein tashrif ley gaey, aapney wahan do rakatein padhein aur ham ne bhi aap ke sath (do rakatein) padhein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab se taweel dua ki, aur jab us se farigh huey to farmaya : ''maine apney rab se teen chizen maangi thin, usney mujhey do ata farma Deen aur eik se mujhey rok diya, maine apney rab se sawal kiya tha ke wo meri ummat ko qehat (sukhe) ke sath halak na karey, usney ye chiz mujhey ata farma di, maine us se ye sawal kiya ke wo meri ummat ko gharq ke zariey halak na karey, to usney ye bhi mujhey ata kar di, aur maine us se sawal kiya ke wo un mein baham (aapas mein) ladaai paida na karey to us se mujhey rok diya gaya.'' rawahu Muslim."
5752,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki, maine kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki us sift ke mutalliq bataeyn jo Torat mein mazkur hai, unhoney farmaya : theek hai, Allah ki qism ! aap ki jo sifaat Quran karim mein hain, un mein se baaz Torat mein mazkur hain, jaisa ke : ''aey Nabi ! ham ne aap ko khushkhabri sunaney wala, daraney wala aur an-padh (arbon) ki hifazat karney wala bana kar bheja hai, aap merey bandey aur merey Rasool hain, maine aap ka naam mutawakkil rakha hai, aap na to bad akhlaq hain aur na sakht dil hain, aap bazaron mein shor aur ghul karney waley hain na burai ka jawab burai se detey hain, balke aap darguzar kartey hain, maaf kartey hain, aur Allah unki rooh qabz nahin karega yahan tak ke wo unke zariey tedhi millat ko sidha kara ley , aur wo ''la Ilaah illallah'' ka iqrar kar lein aur wo us (kalimey) ke zariey andhi aakhon ko quwate beenai (roshni) , behrey kanon ko quwate sama'at (sun'ne ki taqat) aur ghilaf mein band dilon ko khol dega.'' Bukhari."
5753,"Aur isi tarah Darmi ne Ata an ibne Salam ki sanad se usi jaisi riwayat ki hai, aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (نحن الآخرون . . . . .)  ''باب الجمعۃ'' mein zikr ki gaee hai. (rawahu Darmi)."
5754,"Hazrat Khabbab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhaai to usey taweel (lamba) kiya, Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney hamein Namaz padhaai , jabkey aapney aisi Namaz (pehley kabhi) nahin padhaai thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''theek hai, ye ummid aur khof wali Namaz hai, maine is mein Allah Taala se teen chizon ki darkhast ki : usney mujhey do ata farma den aur eik se rok diya, maine us se darkhast ki ke wo qehat (sukhe) ke zariey meri ummat ko halak nahin karega usney usey sharfe-qubuliyat bakhsha , maine us se darkhast ki ke wo unke ilawa kisi aur dushman ko un par musallat nahin karega, usney ye bhi puri farma di aur maine us se ye bhi darkhast ki ke unki aapas mein ladaai (khana jangi) na ho to usney us se mujhey rok diya.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
5755,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne tumhen teen chizon se mehfooz rakha hai, tumhara Nabi tumharey liye ye badduaa nahin karega ke tum sab halak ho jaao , ehle batil , ehle haq par ghalib nahin hongey, aur tum gumrahi par ikhattey nahin hogey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5756,"Hazrat Auf bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah is ummat par do talwaarein jama nahin kerega, eik unki apni talwaar aur eik uskey dushman ki talwaar (yani aisa nahin hoga ke musalmanon mein khana jangi bhi ho aur dushman bhi un par hamla aawar ho).'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5757,"Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo (ghussay ki haalat mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye goya unhoney kuchh (nasab mein taane) suna tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey huey to farmaya : ''main kon hun?'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, aap Allah ke Rasool hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Muhammad bin Abdullah bin abdul Muttalib hun, Allah Taala ne mujhey un mein se behtar giroh mein paida farmaya , phir usney unke qabiley banaey to mujhey un sab se behtar qabiley mein paida farmaya , phir unko gharaney gharaney banaya to mujhey un mein se behtareen gharaney mein paida farmaya , main un se nafs aur hasab ke lihaz se bhi behtar hun aur unke gharaney ke lihaz se bhi behtar hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5758,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap nabuwat ke mansab se kab nawazey gaey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Adam (Alaihissalam) rooh aur jism ke beech they.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5759,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main to us waqt se Allah Taala ke yahan khaatimun Nabiyeen likha hua hun jab Adam (Alaihissalam) abhi (dhaanchey ki haalat mein) mitti ki surat mein padey huey they, aur main abhi apney mamley (yani nabuwat) ke barey main tumhen batata hun, main Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki dua, Esa (Alaihissalam) ki basharat aur apni walida ka wo khuwab hun jo unhoney meri paidaish ke qarib dekha tha ke unke liye eik Noor zahir hua jis se Sham ke mehlaat unke samney roshan ho gaey.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5760,Aur Imam Ahmed ne isey Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se (سأخبر کم) se lekar aakhir hadees tak riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed.
5761,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main roze-qiyamat Adam (Alaihissalam) ki aulad ka sardar hunga , aur main ye az-raah fakhr nahin kehta , hamd ka jhanda merey haath mein hoga, aur main ye baat az-raah fakhr nahin kehta , us roz Adam (Alaihissalam) samet tamam Anbiya (Alaihissalam) merey jhandey taley hongey, sab se pehley mujhey qabr se uthaya jaeyga, aur main ye baat az-raah fakhr nahin kehta.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5762,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kuchh Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bethey huey they. aap bahar se tashrif laye aur unke qarib ho gaey to aapney unhen baaten kartey huey suna, kisi ne kaha : Allah Taala ne Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko khaleel banaya , doosrey ne kaha : Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) se kalam farmaya , kisi aur ne kaha : Esa (Alaihissalam) to wo Allah ka kalima aur uski rooh hain, kisi ne kaha : Adam (Alaihissalam) ko ki Allah ne unhen muntakhab farmaya is doran Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas pahunch gaey aur farmaya : ''maine tumhari baaten sun li hain, aur tumhara tajjub karna ke Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) , Allah ke khaleel hain, aur wo isi tarah hain, Musa (Alaihissalam) kaleemul-llah hain, wo bhi isi tarah hain, Esa (Alaihissalam) uski rooh aur uska kalima hain, wo bhi isi tarah baja hain, Adam (Alaihissalam) ko Allah Taala ne muntakhab farmaya hai, ye bhi haqiqat hai, jabkey main Allah Taala ka Habib hun, aur main ye baat fakhr se nahin kehta , roze-qiyamat hamd ka parcham merey haath mein hoga, Adam (Alaihissalam) aur baqi sab Anbiya (Alaihissalam) usi ke nichey hongey aur main ye baat az-raah fakhr nahin kehta , roze-qiyamat main sab se pehley sifarish karunga aur sab se pehley meri sifarish qubul hogi , aur ye main az-raah fakhr nahin kehta , sab se pehley main hi jannat ke kundey hilaaunga to Allah Taala merey liye khol dega aur mujhey is mein dakhil farmaeyga , merey sath gharib imandar hongey aur main is par fakhr nahin karta, Allah Taala ke yahan tamam awwaleen aur aakhirin se sab se ziyada moazziz main hun aur main is par fakhr nahin karta.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
5763,"Hazrat Amr bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham (duniya mein) aakhir mein aaney waley hain, aur roze-qiyamat (jannat mein dakhil honey walon mein) ham sab se aagey hongey, main kisi fakhr ke baghair ye baat kehta hun ke Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) Allah Taala ke khaleel hain, Musa (Alaihissalam) Safeeullah hain aur main Habibullah hun, roze-qiyamat hamd ka parcham merey sath hoga, Allah Taala ne meri ummat ke mutalliq mujh se wada farma rakha hai, aur usney unhen teen chizon se mehfooz rakha hai, wo unhen aam qehat (sukhe) mein mubtala nahin karega, dushman usko mukammal taur par khatam nahin kar sakega, aur wo un sab ko gumrahi par jama nahin karega.'' rawahu Darmi."
5764,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tamam Rasulon ka qaaid hun, ye baat main fakhr se nahin kehta , main aakhiri Nabi hun, fakhr se nahin kehta , main sab se pehley sifarish karunga aur sab se pehley meri sifarish qubul ki jaeygi aur main ye baat fakhr se nahin kehta.'' rawahu Darmi."
5765,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab logon ko (qabron sey) uthaya jaeyga to main sab se pehley niklunga , jab wo Allah Taala ke huzur pesh hongey to main unka qaaid hunga, jab wo khamosh hongey to main unki taraf se baat karunga, jab unhen rok liya jaeyga (hisab shuru nahin hoga) to main unki sifarish karunga, jab wo na-umeed ho jaeyngey to main unhen (maghfirat aur rehmat ki) khushkhabri sunaunga , karaamat aur chabiyan us roz merey haath mein hongi , us roz hamd ka jhanda merey haath mein hoga, merey rab ke yahan tamam insanon se meri sab se ziyada izzat hogi , hazar khaadim merey ird-gird chakkar laga rahey hongey, goya wo poshida (band kiye huey) anday hain, ya bikhrey huey moti hain.'' Tirmizi, Darmi , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi ."
5766,"HazratAabu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey eik jannati joda pehnaya jaeyga, phir main arsh ke daain taraf khada hunga, aur merey ilawa makhluq mein se koi aur us maqam par khada nahin hoga.'' Tirmizi. aur Jaame al-usool mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai : ''sab se pehley mujhey qabr se uthaya jaeyga aur mujhey joda pehnaya jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5767,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala se merey liye wasila talab karo.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! wasila kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat main eik aa'laa darja hai, wo sirf eik hi aadmi ko nasib hoga, aur main ummid karta hun ke wo main hi hunga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5768,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab roze-qiyamat hoga to main Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ka Imam hunga , unka khateeb aur (maqame Mehmood par) unka sahibe-shafa'at hunga, aur main ye baat fakhr se nahin kehta.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5769,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ke liye Anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se eik (nabi) rafeeq hai, aur merey liye rafeeq , merey baap aur merey rab ke khaleel (Ibrahim (Alaihissalam)) hain.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''be-shak Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke tamam logon mein se ziyada haq daar aur qaribi wo log hain, jinhonne unki ittiba ki aur ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur wo log hain jo eman laye, aur Allah Taala mominon ka dost aur himayati hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5770,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne makaarime-akhlaq ke mukammal karney aur achchhe kamon ko kamaal tak pahunchaney ke liye , mujhey Nabi banakar bheja hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5771,"Hazrat Kab (Raziallahu anhu) Torat se naqal kartey hain ke ham Torat mein ye likha hua paatey hain : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, merey muntakhab bandey hain, wo na to bad akhlaq hain aur na sakht dil , na bazaron mein shor aur ghul karney waley hain aur na burai ka badla burai se detey hain, balke wo darguzar kartey aur maaf kar detey hain, unki jaey (jagah) paidaish Makka hai, unki hijrat tayiba (Madina) ki taraf hogi , unki hukumat mulk Sham mein hogi , unki ummat bahut ziyada hamd karney wali hogi , wo khushhali aur tangdasti (her haal) mein her jagah Allah Taala ki hamd bayan karengey, her buland jagah par Allah Taala ki takbir bayan karengey, wo (namazon ke oqaat ke liye) Suraj ka khayal rakhtey hongey, jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaeyga to wo Namaz padhengey, unka izaar nisf pindliyon tak hoga, wo wuzu ke angon tak wuzu karengey, unka Muazzan buland jagah par (khada ho kar) Azan dega, unki Namaz ke doran safein aur unki maidane-jihad mein safein barabar hongi, aur raat ke waqt un (tahajjud ke waqt tasbih aur tahleel) ki aawaz is tarah hogi jis tarah shehad ki makkhi ki aawaz hoti hai.'' ye alfaz Masaabeh ke hain, aur Imam Darmi ne thodi si tabdili ke sath isey riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi."
5772,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Torat mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sift likhi hui hai aur Esa (Alaihissalam) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath dafn kiye jaeyngey.'' Abu Maudood (raawi) ne bayan kiya : (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke) ghar main eik qabr ki jagah baqi hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5773,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tamam Anbiya (Alaihissalam) aur aasman walon par fazilat ata farmaee hai. unhoney kaha : Abu Abbas ! Allah Taala ne aap ko aasman walon par kis chiz se fazilat ata farmaee hai? unhoney farmaya : Allah Taala ne aasman walon se farmaya : ''un mein se jisney kaha ke main Allah Taala ke siwa mabud hun to ham usey jahannam ki saza dengey, ham isi tarah zalimon ko saza detey hain.'' aur Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se farmaya : ''ham ne aap ko Fateh mubeen ata farmaee taa-ke Allah aap ke tamam gunah maaf farma de.'' unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki doosrey Anbiya (Alaihissalam) par kon si fazilat hai? unhoney kaha : Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''ham ne her Rasool ko uski qom ki zaban ke sath Nabi banakar bheja taa-ke wo unhen wazahat kar sakey, Allah Taala jisey chahta hai gumrah kar deta hai.'' jabkey Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se farmaya : ''ham ne aap ko tamam insanon ki taraf Nabi banakar bheja.'' so Allah Taala ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tamam jinnon aur tamam insanon ki taraf Nabi banakar bheja. rawahu Darmi aur al-Hakim."
5774,"Hazrat Abu-Zar Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney kaisey jana ke aap Nabi hain, yahan tak ke aapney yaqin kar liya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! merey paas do farishtey aaye jabkey main Makka ki wadi Bat'haa mein tha, un mein se eik zamin par utar aaya aur doosra aasman aur zamin ke darmiyan tha, un mein se eik ne apney sathi se kaha : kya ye wohi hain? usney kaha : haan , usney kaha : unka eik aadmi ke sath wazan karen, mera uskey sath wazan kiya gaya to main is par bhari tha, phir usney kaha : inka das afrad ke sath wazan karo, mera unke sath wazan kiya gaya to main un par bhari raha , phir usney kaha : inka sau afrad ke sath wazan karo, mera unke sath wazan kiya gaya to main un par bhi bhari raha , phir usney kaha : inka eik hazar ke sath wazan karo, mera unke sath wazan kiya gaya to main un par bhi bhari raha , goya tarazu ke halkey honey ki wajeh sey, main unhen dekh raha hun ke wo mujh par gir paden-gey.'' farmaya : ''un dono mein se eik ne apney sathi se kaha : agar tum ne unka unki puri ummat ke sath bhi wazan kar liya to ye us (ummat) par ghalib aa jaeyngey.'' dono hadison ko Imam Darmi ne riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi."
5775,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qurbani karna mujh par farz kiya gaya hai, jabkey tum par farz nahin kiya gaya, aur Namaz chaasht ka mujhey hukm diya gaya hai jabkey tumhen uska hukm nahin diya gaya.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni."
5776,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''merey bahut se naam hain : main Muhammad hun, main Ahmed hun, main Maahi hun Allah merey zariey kufr ko mita dega , main Haashir hun ke tamam log merey baad uthaey jaeyngey, aur Main Aaqib hun.'' aur Aaqib usey kehtey hain jiskey baad koi Nabi na ho. muttafaq aleh."
5777,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni zaat mubaraka ke naam hamein bataya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Muhammad hun, main Ahmed hun, main aakhir par aaney wala hun, (merey baad koi Nabi nahi), main Haashir hun, main Nabi tauba hun ( Allah ke huzur bahut ziyada ruju karney wala) aur Nabi rehmat hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
5778,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum tajjub nahin kartey ke Allah Quraish ke sab aur shitam aur unke laanat-malamat karney ko kis tarah mujh se door karta hai? wo muzammam (naauzubillah jiski mazammat ki gaee ho) keh kar sab aur shitam aur laanat-malamat kartey hain, jabkey main Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hun.'' Bukhari."
5779,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar Mubarak aur dadhi ke agley hissey ke kuchh baal safed ho chukey they, jab aap tel lagatey they to wo nazar nahin aatey they, aur jab aap ke sar ke baalon mein kanghi nahin ki hoti thi to wo nazar aa jatey they, aap ki dadhi ke baal ghaney they, kisi aadmi ne kaha : aap ka chehra Mubarak (chamak ke lihaz sey) talwaar ki tarah tha, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : nahin, balke Suraj aur chaand ki tarah chamakta tha, rukh anwar gol tha, maine aap ke kandhey ke paas nabuwat ki mohar dekhi jo ke kabootri ke anday ki tarah thi aur wo aap ke jism at'har (ke rang) ke mushabeh thi. rawahu Muslim."
5780,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aur aap ke sath gosht roti khai , ya kaha : sareed khai , phir main ghoom kar aap ke pichli janib gaya aur maine aap ke dono kandhon ke darmiyan baain kandhey ki naram haddi ke paas nabuwat ki mohar dekhi, wo band mutthi ki tarah thi is par do til they, jaisey massey hon.'' rawahu Muslim."
5781,"Hazrat Umme-Khalid binte Khalid bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuchh kapdey laye gaey un main eik chhoti si kaali chadar thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Khalid ko merey paas laao, usey utha kar laya gaya, aapney apney daste Mubarak se wo chadar pakdi aur usey pehna di, aur farmaya : ''tum isey boseedah karo aur tum isey puraanaa karo (der tak jeeti raho), tum isey boseedah karo aur isey puraanaa karo.'' us (chadar) mein sabz (hara) ya zard rang ke nishaanaat they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Khalid ! ye ''sanaah'' hai.'' aur ye (sanaah) Habshi zaban ka lafz hai yani khoobsurat? wo bayan karti hain, main mohare nabuwat ke sath khelney lagi to merey walid ne mujhey daantaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey chhod do.'' Bukhari."
5782,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada lambey qad ke they na chhotey qad ke na bilkul safed they aur na gandumi rang ke , aap ke baal na bahut ziyada ghungariyaaley they na sidhey, Allah Taala ne aap ko chaalis saal ki umr mein Nabi banakar bheja, aapney Makka mein das saal qiyam farmaya aur Madina mein bhi das saal qiyam farmaya , aur Allah Taala ne aap ko saath saal ki umr mein wafat di aur (us waqt) aap ke sar aur dadhi mein bees baal bhi safed nahin they. eik dusri riwayat mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke osaaf bayan kartey huey farmaya : aap ka qad darmiyana tha na lamba tha aur na chhota, khultaa aur chamakta hua rang tha, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal kanon ke nisf (aadhe) tak they, eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal dono kanon aur kandhon ke darmiyan they. aur Sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sar aur paaon zakheem (mote) they, maine aap ke baad ya pehley aap jaisa koi doosra shakhs nahin dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hatheliyan kushada thin, Sahih Bukhari ki dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paaon aur haath motey they. muttafaq aleh."
5783,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) darmiyaney qad ke they, aap ki chhaati kushada thi, aap ke sar ke baal kanon ki lo tak they, maine aap ko surkh jodey mein dekha, maine aap se ziyada Husain kisi ko nahin dekha. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, maine kanon ki lo tak baalon waley aur surkh jodey mein malboos kisi shakhs ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada Husain nahin dekha aap ke baal aap ke kandhon par padtey they, aap ki chhaati kushada thi, aur aap na ziyada lambey they aur na chhotey they. muttafaq aleh."
5784,"Hazrat Simaak bin Harab , Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ضلیع الفم ، اشکل العین aur منھوش العقبین they. Simaak (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, ضلیع الفم se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : kushada chehrey waley, puchha gaya, اشکل العین se kya murad hai? farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aankhen badi aur taweel thin, phir puchha gaya : منھوش العقبین se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki edhiyaan patli thin. rawahu Muslim."
5785,"Hazrat Abu Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai aap ki rangat surkhi maael safed thi aur aap ka qad darmiyana tha. rawahu Muslim."
5786,"Hazrat Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khizaab ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : aap ke baal is qadr safed nahin they ke unhen khizaab kiya jata, agar main aap ki dadhi ke safed baal gin'naa chahta , to gin sakta tha. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : agar main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar ke safed baal gin'naa chahta to gin sakta tha. aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke عنفقہ (nichley hont aur thodi ke darmiyan) mein , aap ki kan pattiyon mein aur aap ke sar mein chand safed baal they. muttafaq aleh."
5787,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki rangat mein chamak damak thi aap ke paseeney ke qatrey motiyon ki tarah they, jab aap chaltey to aagey ki taraf jhuk kar chaltey they, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hatheli se ziyada naram, deebaaj aur resham ko bhi nahin paya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke badan at'har se ziyada mua'ttar (khushbudar), kastoori ya anbar ki khushbu nahin soonghi. muttafaq aleh."
5788,"Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan tashrif laya kartey aur wahin qailula farmaya kartey they, wo chamdey ki chatai bicha detin aur aap is par qailula farmatey, aap ko paseena bahut aata tha, wo aap ka paseena jama kar letiin aur phir usey khushbu mein shamil kar letin, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Sulaim ! ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya : aap ka paseena hai, ham isey apni khushbu ke sath mila letey hain, aap ka paseena eik behtareen khushbu hai, eik dusri riwayat mein hai. unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham uskey zariey apney bachon ke liye barkat hasil kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne theek kiya.'' muttafaq aleh."
5789,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz uoola (Fajr ya zohar) padhi , phir aap apney ehle khana ki taraf tashrif ley gaey, main bhi aap ke sath hi (masjid sey) nikal aaya, raastey mein kuchh bachchey aap se miley to aapney baari baari unke rukhsaaron par daste shafqat phera jabkey aapney merey dono rukhsaaron par daste shafqat phera. maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke dast Mubarak ki thandak aur khushbu aisey mehsus ki goya aapney usey attaar ke dibbey se nikala hai. rawahu Muslim. Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ( سموا باسمی. . . . .) ''baab al-asaamii'' mein aur Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ( نظرت الیٰ خاتم النبوۃ . . .) ''باب احکام المیاہ'' mein bayan ki gaee hai."
5790,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lambey qad ke they na chhotey qad ke, sar Mubarak zakheem(mota) tha, dadhi ghani thi, haath aur paaon bhari they, surkh aur safed rang tha, haddiyon ke jod mazbut they, aap ke seeney se naaf tak baalon ki lambi lakeer thi, jab aap chaltey to aagey ko jhukey hotey goya aap bulandi se nichey utar rahey hain, aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein aap jaisa koi dekha na aap ke baad . Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5791,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke osaaf bayan kartey to farmatey : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada lambey they na ziyada chhotey they balke aap darmiyana qad they, aap ke baal bilkul ghungariyaaley they na bilkul sidhey balke un dono Suraton ke darmiyan they, aap ka chehra Mubarak bilkul gol nahin tha, balke qadrey golaee mein tha, aap ka rang surkhi maael safed tha, aankhen siyah , daraz (lambi) palke, jodon ki haddiyan uthi hui mazbut thin, kandhon ka darmiyani hissey bhi bada aur mazbut tha, aap ke badan par baal nahin they, bas seeney aur naaf tak eik lakeer thi, haath aur paaon bhari they, jab aap chaltey to paaon utha kar rakhtey goya aap bulandi se utar rahey hain, jab aap kisi ki taraf tawajjoh to mukammal tawajjoh farmatey, aap ke kandhon ke darmiyan mehar nabuwat thi, aur aap aakhiri Nabi hain, aap sab se badh kar dil ke sakhi they, sab se ziyada saaf bhale hi they, sab se ziyada naram mizaj they, qabiley ke lihaz se sab se ziyada moazziz they, jo aap ko achchhaa dekhta to wo heybat zada ho jata, jo aap ki sohbat ikhtiyar karta aur waqfiyat hasil kar leta to wo aap se toot kar mohabbat karney lagta , aur aap ki khoobi bayan karney wala (aakhir par) ye kehta : maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaisa aap ki hayaat mubaraka mein koi dekha na aap ke baad. rawahu Tirmizi."
5792,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis raah se guzar jatey to aap ke baad us raah se guzarney wala aap ki khushbu se ya aap ke mua'ttar(khushbudar) paseeney se pehchan leta ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yahan se guzrey hain. rawahu Darmi.
5793,"Hazrat Abu Ubeda bin Muhammad bin Ammar bin Yasir bayan kartey hain, maine Rabeea binte-Muawwiz bin Ifra (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke osaaf se aagah karen, unhoney farmaya : bete ! agar tum unhen dekhtey to tum (unke chehrey Mubarak ko) chamakta hua Suraj dekhtey. rawahu Darmi."
5794,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine chaandni raat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to main (baari baari) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur chaand ki taraf dekhney laga, aapney surkh joda pehne hua tha, aur us waqt meri nazar mein aap chaand se bhi ziyada khoobsurat they. rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
5795,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada Husain chiz koi nahin dekhi , goya aap ke chehrey Mubarak par Suraj jalwa rez hai, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada tez raftaar kisi ko nahin dekha goya aap ke liye zamin lapeti ja rahi hai, ham puri tarah tez chalney ki koshish kartey lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) parwa kiye baghair chaltey rehtey (phir bhi ham aap tak nahin pahunch saktey they). rawahu Tirmizi."
5796,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki pindliyan patli thin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sirf tabassum farmaya kartey they, jab main aap ko dekhta to main kehta ke aapney aakhon mein surma lagaya hua hai, halanke aapney surma nahin lagaya hota tha. rawahu Tirmizi."
5797,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney ke do daant kushada they, jab aap guftgu farmatey to aisey malum hota ke aap ke do daanton se Noor baras raha hai. rawahu Darmi."
5798,"Hazrat Kab bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khush hotey they to aap ka chehra chamak jata aur rukh anwar aisey lagta jaisey ke wo chaand ka tukda hai aur ham ye chiz pehchan letey they. muttafaq aleh."
5799,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ladka , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kiya karta tha, wo bimar ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey aapney uskey walid ko uskey sar ke paas Torat padhtey dekh kar farmaya : ''aey Yahudi ! main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun jisney Musa (Alaihissalam) par Torat nazil farmaee, (bataao) kya tum Torat mein meri zaat aur sifaat ke mutalliq kuchh likha hua paatey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin lekin wo ladka kehney laga , Allah ki qism ! Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaat aur sifaat aur aap ki tashrif aawri ke mutalliq Torat mein likha hua paatey hain, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur aap Allah ke Rasool hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba se farmaya : ''usko us (ladkey) ke sarhaaney se utha do aur tum apney (Islaami) bhai ki (tajheez aur takfeen ke mutalliq) sar parasti karo.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi)."
5800,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bheji hui rehmat hun.'' (rawahu Darmi aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5801,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine das saal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat ki, lekin aapney mujhey kabhi uff tak na kaha, aur na hi ye kaha ke to ne ye kaam kyon kiya aur wo kaam kyon nahin kiya. muttafaq aleh."
5802,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tamam logon se behtareen akhlaq ke hamil they, aapney eik roz mujhey kisi kaam ke liye bheja to maine kaha, Allah ki qism ! main nahin jaaunga , jabkey merey dil mein tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jis kaam ka mujhey hukm farmaya hai main uskey liye zarur jaaunga, main nikla , aur chand aisey bachchon ke paas se guzra jo baazar mein khel rahey they. (main wahan khada ho gaya) itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey peechhey se meri guddi pakad li , wo bayan kartey hain, maine aap ki taraf dekha to aap hans rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Unnees ! jahan janey ke mutalliq maine tumhen kaha tha, kya wahan gaey ho?'' maine arz kiya : ji haan , Allah ke Rasool ! main ja raha hun. rawahu Muslim."
5803,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chal raha tha, aap par motey kinarey (chodi patti) wali najraani chadar thi, itney main eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) aap ke paas aaya aur usney aap ki chadar ke sath aap ko itney zor se khincha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ke seeney ke qarib pahunch gaey, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kandhey par dekha to zor se khinchney ki wajeh se chadar ke kinarey ke nishaanaat kandhey Mubarak par pad chukey they, phir usney kaha : Muhammad ! Allah ka maal jo aap ke paas hai is mein se merey liye bhi hukm farmaiye, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha, aur hans diye , phir usey kuchh deney ka hukm farmaya.'' muttafaq aleh."
5804,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sab se ziyada Haseen, sab se ziyada sakhi aur sab se ziyada bahaadur they, eik raat Madina waley ghabra gaey to log uski aawaz ki taraf chal padey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sab se pehley uski aawaz ki taraf gaey they aur wapsi par aap logon se miley to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghabraow nahin, ghabraow nahin.'' aap us waqt Abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghodey ki nangi peeth par Sawar they, is par zeen nahin thi aur aap ke galey mein talwaar thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine is (ghodey) ko nihayat tez raftaar paya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5805,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kabhi aisey nahin hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kisi chiz ka sawal kiya gaya aur aapney nafi mein jawab diya ho. muttafaq aleh."
5806,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se itni bakriyan maangin jis se do pahadon ka darmiyani fasla bhar jaey, aapney itni hi usey dey den to wo apni qom ke paas gaya aur unhen kaha : meri qom ! Islam qubul kar lo , Allah ki qism ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr ata farmatey hain ke wo faqr (gharibi) ka andesha nahin rakhtay. (ya faqr ka andesha nahin rehta) rawahu Muslim."
5807,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, is beech mein ke ghazwae-Hunain se wapsi par wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chal rahey they, (raastey mein) Erabi (dehati) (dehati) chimat kar aap se sawal karney lagey, yahan tak ke unhoney aap ko babool ke darkht ki taraf dhakel diya, wo (kaantey) aap ki chadar se ulajh gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey ho kar farmaya : ''meri chadar mujhey dey do, agar merey paas in (kaantey-daar) darakhton jitney oont hotey to main wo bhi tumharey darmiyan taqseem kar deta, lihaza tum mujhey bakheel paaogey na jhoota aur na buzdil.'' Bukhari."
5808,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab subah ki Namaz padh letey to Madina ke khaadim apney bartan ley aatey , un mein pani hota tha, wo jo bhi bartan latey , aap is mein apna dast Mubarak dubo detey they, kabhi-kabhi to wo sardi ke mosam mein subah ke waqt aap ke paas aa jatey they, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is mein apna haath dubo diya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
5809,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Madiney walon ki laundiyon mein koi bhi londi wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath pakadti aur wo jahan chahti aap ko ley jati thi. Bukhari."
5810,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat thi jiski aql kuchh kam thi, usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey aap se kuchh kaam hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme- falan ! dekho ! jis gali main tum chaho main tumharey sath chalta hun ta ke main tumhara kaam pura kar sakoon, aap eik raastey mein uskey sath gaey yahan tak ke uska kaam ho gaya. rawahu Muslim."
5811,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) na gandi baat karte they na lanat karney waley they, aur na hi gaali detey they, narazi ke aalim mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bas yehi farmatey : ''usey kya hua? uski peshani khaak aalud ho.'' Bukhari."
5812,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! mushrikon ke liye badduaa farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey lanat karney ke liye nahin bheja gaya, mujhey to baaise rehmat bana kar bheja gaya hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5813,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) parda nasheen kanwari ladkiyon se bhi ziyada sharmeeley they, jab aap koi aisi chiz dekhtey jo aap ko nagawar guzarti to ham usey aap ke chehrey Mubarak se pehchan letey they. muttafaq aleh."
5814,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is tarah khil-khila kar hanstay huey kabhi nahin dekha ke aap ke halaq ka aakhiri hissey dekh sakun kyonkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sirf tabassum farmaya kartey they. Bukhari."
5815,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhari tarah nihayat tez guftgu nahin farmatey they, balke aap is tarah guftgu farmatey they ke agar koi (alfaz) shumar karney wala shumar karna chahta to shumar kar sakta tha. muttafaq aleh."
5816,"Hazrat Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kiya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar mein kya kiya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap apney ehale khana ki khidmat mein masroof rehtey they, jab Namaz ka waqt ho jata to aap Namaz ke liye tashrif ley jatey they. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari."
5817,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko do kamon mein se eik ka ikhtiyar diya jata to aap un dono mein se aasan tar ko ikhtiyar farmatey they, ba-sharte ke wo gunah ka kaam na hota, agar is mein gunah hota to aap sab se ziyada us se door rehtey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni zaat ke mutalliq kisi mamley mein intiqam nahin liya, agar Allah ki hudood paamaal ki jatin to aap is mein Allah ki raza ki khatir intiqam liya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
5818,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ki raah mein jihad karney ke ilawa apney haath se kisi chiz ko maara na kisi khaadim ko aur na hi kisi aurat ko , aur agar aap ko kisi ki taraf se koi takleef pahunchti to aap us takleef pahunchaney waley se intiqam nahin letey they, aap sirf us surat mein intiqam letey they jab Allah ki hudood paamaal hoti hon aur wo intiqam bhi mehaz Allah ki raza ki khatir hi letey they. rawahu Muslim."
5819,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aath baras ki umr mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat ke liye hazir hua aur das saal aap ki khidmat ki, aapney us arsey mein merey haathon honey waley kisi nuqsan par mujhey malamat nahin ki, agar aap ke ehale khana mein se koi mujhey malamat karta to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''isey chhod do, kyonkey jo taqdir mein likh diya gaya hai wo ho kar rehta hai.'' ye alfaz hadees Masaabeh ke hain, aur Imam Behaqi ne kuchh tabdili ke sath Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5820,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)  na jaan bujh kar gandi baat karte aur na anjane mein karte they, aap bazaron mein shor aur ghul kartey they na burai ka badla burai se detey they, balke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) darguzar farmatey they, aur maaf farma detey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
5821,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees bayan kartey hain ke aap bimaron ki iyaadat kartey they, janaazon mein shareek hotey they, ghulamon ki dawat qubul kartey they, aur gadhey par sawari kartey they, khaibar ke din maine aap ko gadhey par dekha jiski lagaam khajoor ke patton ki thi. (rawahu ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5822,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna joota marammat kartey they, apna kapda khud si letey they aur apney ghar mein tumhari tarah hi kaam kartey they. aur unhoney farmaya : aap bhi eik insan they, aap apney kapdey mein juein dekh liya kartey they, apni bakri ka doodh khud dohtey they aur apney zaati kaam khud kiya kartey they. (rawahu Tirmizi فی الشمائل و البخاری فی الأدب المفرد)."
5823,"Hazrat khaarija bin Zaid bin Sabit bayan kartey hain, kuchh afrad Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye to unhoney un se kaha, aap hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadisen sunaao, unhoney kaha, main aap ka padosi tha, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ""wahi"" nazil hoti to aap mujhey bulatey aur main ""wahi"" ko likh deta tha, jab ham duniya ka zikr kartey they to aap hamarey sath uska zikr farmatey they, jab ham aakhirat ka zikr kartey to aap hamarey sath uska zikr farmatey they, aur jab ham khaney ka zikr kartey to aap hamarey sath khaney ka zikr farmatey they. main ye sari baaten tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kar raha hun. (rawahu Tirmizi fi Shamail w fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5824,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aadmi se musaafa farmatey they to aap uskey haath se apna haath nahin chhudaatey they yahan tak ke wo aadmi khud apna haath chuda leta tha, aap apna chehra Mubarak (tawajjoh) us shakhs se nahin hataatey they yahan tak ke wo shakhs khud apna chehra aap ke chehre Mubarak se hata leta (kisi aur taraf mutawajjeh kar leta) aur aap ko majlis mein apney ham nasheen se aagey ghutney nikal kar bethey huey nahin dekha gaya. rawahu Tirmizi."
5825,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni zaat ke liye kisi chiz ka zakhira nahin kiya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi.
5826,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada tar khamosh raha kartey they, (bila zarurat koi baat nahin farmatey they). (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5827,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kalam mein tarteel (thahar-thahar kar) aur tehraaow tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5828,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhari tarah nihayat tez guftgu nahin farmatey they, balke aap ka kalam alag alag hota tha, aap ke paas bethney wala usey yad kar leta tha. rawahu Tirmizi."
5829,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada kisi ko muskuraatey huey nahin dekha. rawahu Tirmizi."
5830,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab guftgu farmaney ke liye bethtey to aap (nuzool ""wahi"" ke intizar mein) aasman ki taraf bahut dekhtey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5831,"Hazrat Amr bin Saeed, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada kisi ko apney bachchon ke sath meharban nahin dekha, aap ke bete Ibrahim Madiney ke dehat mein zere-raza'at (doodh pitey) they, aap (wahan) tashrif ley jaya kartey they, ham bhi aap ke sath hotey they, aap us ghar mein dakhil ho jatey , is mein dhuwan hota tha, kyonkey Ibrahim ki daaya ka shohar lohaar tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey pakadtey uska bosa letey aur phir wapis aa jatey they. Amr bayan kartey hain, jab Ibrahim faut huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera beta Ibrahim chunkey sheer-khwaargi ke aalim mein faut hua hai isliye jannat mein uskey liye do daaya hain jo doodh pilane ki muddat puri kerengi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5832,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke falan naam se Mausum eik Yahudi aalim tha, uska Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par kuch Dinar qarz tha, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se taqaza kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''yahudi ! tumhen deney ke liye merey paas kuchh nahin.'' usney kaha : Muhammad ! main to lekar hi yahan se hilunga, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achchhaa phir main tumharey sath beth jata hun.'' aap uskey sath beth gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zohar, asr, maghrib, Isha aur Fajr ki Namaz uskey sath ada ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba usey daratey dhamkaatey rahey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Sahaba kiram ke is amal ki ittilaa ho gaee , to unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! eik Yahudi ne aap ko rok rakha hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey rab ne kisi zimmi waghera par zulm karney se mujhey mana farmaya hai.'' jab Suraj buland hua (din chadha) to us Yahudi ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke Rasool hain. mera nisf (aadha) maal Allah ki raah mein waqf hai? sun lo , Allah ki qism ! maine aap ke sath jo ravaiya ikhtiyar kiya wo mehaz isliye kiya ta ke main Torat mein aap ka mazkura Taaruf : dekh sakoon, Muhammad bin Abdullah unki jaey (jagah) paidaish Makka, daar hijrat tayiba (Madina Munawwara), unki saltanat Sham tak, wo bad zaban hain na sakht dil aur na hi bazaron mein shor aur ghul karney waley hain, wo na ganda pehante hain na gandi baate karne wale, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur ye ke aap Allah ke Rasool hain, aur ye maal hai aap Allah ke ehkamat ki roshni mein is mein jis tarah chahen tasarruf (dakhal) farmaeyn, aur Yahudi bahut ziyada maal daar tha. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaailun-nubuwa)."
5833,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zikr kasrat se kiya kartey they, be maqsad baat bahut hi kam kiya kartey they, Namaz (khas taur par Juma ki Namaz) lambi padha kartey they. khutba mukhtasar diya kartey they, aap bewaaon aur miskinon ke sath chalney mein koi aar (sharm) mehsus nahin kartey they aur aap unke kaam kartey aur unki zarooratein puri kartey they. rawahu Nasai aur Darmi."
5834,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Abu-Jahal ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : ham aap ko nahin jhutlate balke ham to us chiz ki jhutlate hain, jo aap lekar aaye hain, tab Allah Taala ne unke mutalliq ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''ye log aap ko nahin jhtlate, balke zalim log Allah ki aayaat ka inkar kartey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5835,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! agar main chahun to soney ke pahad merey sath chalen , eik farishta merey paas aaya, uski kamar (ki chorai) Kaba (ki lambaai) ke barabar thi, usney (aa kar) kaha : tumhara rab tumhen salam kehta hai, aur wo kehta hai : agar aap chahen to aap ko abid Nabi bana detey hain aur agar aap pasand farmaain to aap ko badshah peghambar bana detey hain, maine Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ki taraf dekha to unhoney meri taraf ishara kiya ke apney aap ko past aur aajiz rakho.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5836,"Aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ki taraf dekha jaisey aap un se mashwara kar rahey hain, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne apney haath se ishara kiya ke aap tawaazeh ikhtiyar karen, maine kaha : main ibadat guzar Nabi ban'na pasand karta hun. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, uskey baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tek laga kar nahin khaya kartey they, aur farmaya kartey they : ''main aisey khaunga, jaisey (aam) banda, khata hai, aur main aisey bethunga, jaisey banda bethta hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5837,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko chaalis saal ki umr mein mab-us (bheja) kya gaya, aap (nabuwat ke) tehra saal makkey mein rahey aur aap par ""wahi"" aati rahi , phir aap ko hijrat ka hukm diya gaya to aapney hijrat ke das saal (Madiney mein) qiyam farmaya, aur aapney tiresath baras ki umr mein wafat pai. muttafaq aleh."
5838,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein pandarah baras rahey, aap saat saal tak aawaz suntey aur roshni dekhtey rahey, aur (uskey ilawa) aap koi chiz nahin dekhtey they, aur aath saal aap ki taraf ""wahi"" aati rahi , aapney Madina mein das saal qiyam farmaya : aur painsath baras ki umr mein wafat pai. muttafaq aleh."
5839,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah Taala ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko saath saal mukammal honey par wafat di. muttafaq aleh."
5840,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jab rooh qabz ki gaee to us waqt aap ki umr tiresath baras thi, Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki bhi rooh jab qabz ki gaee to us waqt unki umrein bhi tiresath baras ki thin. rawahu Muslim. Muhammad bin Ismail Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tiresath baras ki umr ke mutalliq riwayaat ziyada hain."
5841,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ""wahi"" ka aaghaz sachey aur pakizah khuwabon se shuru hua, aap jo bhi khuwab dekhtey wo subah ki roshni ki tarah (sachcha) Sabit ho jata, phir aap tanhai pasand ho gaey, aap ghaare-Hiraa mein khilwat farmaya kartey they, aap apney ehale-khana ke paas aaney se pehley kaee kaee raaten wahan ibadat mein mashghool rehtey they, un dinon (dinon) ke liye zaade-raah sath ley jaya kartey they, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif latey aur itni hi muddat ke liye phir zaade-rah sath ley jatey they, yahan tak ke aap ghaare-Hiraa hi mein they ke aap par haq (wahi) aa gaya, farishta (Jibrael (Alaihissalam)) aap ke paas aaya to usney kaha padhiye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main qaari nahin (padhna nahin janta) hun.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney mujhey pakda aur itni shiddat se dabaayaa jis se mujhey kafi takleef hui, phir usney mujhey chhod diya, aur kaha : padhiye, maine kaha : main padhna nahin janta. usney mujhey pakad kar dusri martaba khub dabaayaa, mujhey us baar bhi kafi takleef hui, phir usney mujhey chhod diya, aur kaha : padhiye , maine kaha : main padhna nahin janta , usney mujhey teesri martaba dabaya us baar bhi mujhey kafi takleef hui, phir usney mujhey chhod diya aur kaha : padhiye apney rab ke naam ke sath jisney paida farmaya , usney insan ko jamey huey khoon se paida farmaya, padhiye, aap ka rab bahut hi karam karney wala hai, jisney qalam ke zariey sikhaya, insan ko wo kuchh sikhaya jo wo nahin janta tha'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey baad wapis huey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka dil (khof ki wajeh sey) dhadak raha tha, aap Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif laye, aur farmaya : ''mujhey kambal odha do, mujhey kambal odha do, unhoney aap ko kambal odha diya yahan tak ke aap ka khof jata raha to aapney Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) se sara waqia bayan kiya aur kaha : ''mujhey apni jaan ka andesha hai.'' Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : hergiz nahin, Allah ki qism ! Allah aap ko kabhi ruswa nahin kerega, aap sila rehmi kartey hain, seedhi baat karte hain, dard mandon ka bojh uthatey hain, tahi daston (tukdiyon) ke liye kamatey hain, mehman ki mezbani kartey hain, aur musibat zada afrad ki iaa'nat (madad) kartey hain, phir Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) aap ko apney chacha zaad bhai Warqa bin Nofal ke paas ley gaeen, unhoney un se kaha : merey chacha ke bete ! apney bhatijey ki baat sunen, Warqa ne aap se kaha : bhatijey ! aap kya dekhtey ho? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo dekha tha wo kuchh usey bata diya , Warqa ne kaha : ye to wohi naamoos hai, jisey Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ki taraf ""wahi"" de-kar bheja tha, kaash! ! main us waqt jawan hota, kaash! main us waqt zinda hota jab aap ki qom aap ko nikal deygi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo mujhey nikal dengey?'' usney kaha : haan jab kisi ko mansab nabuwat (nabuwat ke auhde) par faaiz kiya gaya to us se zarur dushmani ki gaee aur agar maine tumhara zamana pa liya to main tumhari zabardast madad karunga, phir Warqa jald hi wafat pa gaey aur kuchh arsa ke liye ""wahi"" ruk gaee. muttafaq aleh."
5842,"Aur Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghamgin ho gaey, hamein jo riwayaat pahunchi hain, unke mutabiq ye hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shadeed ghamgin ho gaey, kaee dafa unke dil mein ye khayal aaya ke wo pahad ki choti se apney aap ko nichey gira lein , wo jab bhi pahad ki choti par pahunch kar apney aap ko giraaney lagtey to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aap ke samney aa jatey aur kehtey : Muhammad ! aap Allah ke sachchay Rasool hain, us se aap ka dili iztirab khatam ho jata aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sukoon mehsus kartey. Bukhari."
5843,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ""wahi"" ke ruk janey ke zamaney ke mutalliq hadees bayan kartey huey suna, farmaya : ''is beech mein ke main chala ja raha tha to maine aasman main eik aawaz suni, maine apni nazar uthai to maine dekha ke wohi farishta jo ghaare-Hiraa mein merey paas aaya tha, aasman aur zamin ke darmiyan eik kursi par betha hua hai, main uskey roab se khof-zada hua aur zamin par gir pada , uskey baad main apney eahle khana ke paas aa gaya, aur maine kaha : mujhey kambal odha do , mujhey kambal odha do, chunanche unhoney mujhey kambal odha diya, phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : '' kambal odh kar letney waley ! uth jaeyn aur logon ko (Azabe-Ilaahi sey) daraeyn , apney rab ki badai bayan karen, apney kapdon ko saaf suthra rakhen aur gandagi se door rahen.'' phir ""wahi"" tezi ke sath pay dar pay (lagatar) aaney lagi.'' muttafaq aleh."
5844,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Haris bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kartey huey arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap par ""wahi"" kaisey aati hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kabhi wo merey paas ghanti ki si aawaz ki surat mein aati hai, aur wo mujh par nihayat sakht hoti hai, aur us se paseena jari ho jata hai, aur jo wo kehta hai, main usey yad kar leta hun, aur kabhi farishta aadmi ki shakal mein merey paas aata hai aur mujh se kalam karta hai, wo jo kehta hai main usey yad kar leta hun.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke shadeed sardi ke din aap par ""wahi"" nazil hoti to aap se paseeney phoot padtey aur aap ki peshani paseeney se sharaborشرابور ho jati. rawahu Muslim."
5845,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ""wahi"" nazil hoti to us wajeh se aap karb (baichaini) mehsus kartey aur aap ke chehra Mubarak ka rang tabdeel ho jata tha. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sar jhuk jata, aur aap ke Sahaba apney sar jhuka letey they, aur jab ""wahi"" khatam ho jati to aap apna sar utha letey they. rawahu Muslim."
5846,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat : ''apney qaribi rishtey daaron ko daraeyn.'' nazil hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye aur Safa par chadh kar aawaz deney lagey : ''banu fahar ! bano Adi !'' aapney Quraish ke qabeelon ko aawaz di, yahan tak ke wo sab jama ho gaey, agar koi aadmi khud nahin aa sakta tha to usney apna numaainda bhej diya tha ta ke wo dekhey ke kya maamla hai, chunanche Abu Lahab aur Quraishi bhi aa gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bataao, agar main tumhen bataaun ke us pahad ke peechhey se eik lashkar aaney wala hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''us wadi ke peechhey eik lashkar hai jo tum par hamla karney wala hai, kya tum mujhey sacha samjhogey?'' unhoney kaha : haan , kyonkey ham ne aap ko sachcha hi paya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main sakht azab sey, jo tumharey samney aa raha hai, tumhen darata hun.'' Abu-Lahab bol utha, (nauzubillah) tum halak ho jaao, tum ne isliye hamen jama kiya tha? Allah Taala ne ye sura nazil farmaee : ''Abu-Lahab ke dono haath toot gaey aur wo barbad ho gaya.'' rawahu Muslim."
5847,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain is beech mein ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaba ke paas Namaz padh rahey they jabkey Quraishi apni majaalis mein bethey huey they ke kisi ne kaha : tum mein se kon falan qabiley ke zibeh kiye huey oonton ke paas jaey aur wo wahan se uska gobar , khoon aur post utha laye, phir wo intizar karey aur jab wo sajdey mein jaeyn to wo un chizon ko unki gardan par rakh dey? chunanche un mein se sab se ziyada bad-bakht shakhs utha, (aur wo sab chizen ley aaya) jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajdey mein gaey to usney wo chizen aap ki gardan par rakh den, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajdey hi ki haalat mein rahey, wo (mushrekin) dekh kar hans rahey they aur hansi ki wajeh se eik doosrey par lot pot ho rahey they, chunanche eik shakhs Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya (aur unhen bataya) to wo daudti hui tashrif laaen, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajdey hi ki haalat mein they Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne us (ghilazat) ko aap se utaar phenka , aur unhen bura bhala kaha, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! to Quraish ko pakad ley, aey Allah ! to Quraish ko pakad ley, aey Allah ! to Quraish ko pakad ley.'' teen baar farmaya, aur aap ka mamool tha ke jab aap dua kartey to teen baar dua kartey they, aur jab (Allah sey) koi chiz talab farmatey to teen baar talab farmatey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Amr bin Hisham , Utba bin Rabeea , Sheba bin Rabeea , Waleed bin Utba , Umayya bin Khalaf , Aqba bin Abi Mueet aur Umara bin Waleed ko pakad ley.'' Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah ki qism ! Badr ke din maine un sab ko maqtool paya , phir unhen ghaseet kar Badr ke kunwen mein phenk diya gaya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qaleeb walon par lanat barsa di gaee.'' muttafaq aleh."
5848,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap par uhad ke din se bhi ziyada sakht koi din guzra hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey tumhari qom ki taraf se bahut se masaayib (pareshaniyon) ka samna karna pada hai, lekin Aqba ke din mujhey unki taraf se bahut takleef pahunchi hai, jab maine ibne Abd ya Laila bin Kalaal par dawat pesh ki aur usney meri dawat qubul na ki, main hairaan aur pareshan wapis chal pada , mujhey malum na tha ke main kis samt chal raha hun, qaarnis saalib par pahunch kar mujhey kuchh pata chala , maine sar uthaya to dekha ke badal ke tukdey ne mujh par saya kiya hua hai, is mein Jibrael (Alaihissalam) hain, unhoney mujhey aawaz di, aur kaha ke Allah ne aap ki qom ki baat aur unka jawab sun liya hai, aur usney pahadon ka farishta aap ki taraf bheja hai ta ke aap unke mutalliq jo chahen hukm farmaeyn.'' farmaya : ''pahadon ke farishtey ne mujhey aawaz di, usney mujhey salam keh kar arz kiya, Muhammad ! Allah ne aap ki qom ki baat sun li hai, aur main pahadon ka farishta hun, aap ke rab ne mujhey aap ki taraf bheja hai ta ke aap jo chahen mujhey hukm farmaeyn, agar aap chahen to main dono taraf ke pahad la kar un par mila dun.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke mujhey ummid hai ke Allah unke salb se aisey log paida farmaeyga jo eik Allah ki ibadat karengey aur wo uskey sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5849,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwae uhad mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney ke chaar daant toot gaey aur aap ka sar Mubarak zakhmi kar diya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khoon saaf kar rahey they aur farma rahey they : ''wo qom kaisey falah paey gi jisney apney Nabi ka sar zakhmi kar diya aur uskey samney ke chaar daant Shahid kar diye.'' rawahu Muslim."
5850,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us qom par sakht naraz hai jisney apney Nabi ke sath aisa sulook kiya.'' aur us se aap ka ishara apney samney ke chaar daanton ki taraf tha, aur aisey shakhs par bhi Allah ka ghazab shadeed hota hai jisey Allah ka Rasul Allah ki raah mein qatl kar dey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5851,"Hazrat Yahya bin Abi Kasir bayan kartey hain, maine Abu Salma bin Abdur Rehman se puchha : Quran ka kon sa hissey sab se pehley nazil hua? unhoney kaha : (یَا اَیُّھَا الْمُدَّثِّرُ) maine kaha : wo (baaz ulamaa) kehtey hain :  (اِقْرَأْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّکَ) Abu-Salma ne farmaya : maine Jabir se uskey mutalliq puchha tha, aur maine bhi un se isi tarah kaha tha jis tarah tum ne mujhey kaha hai, to Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke main tumhen wohi kuch bayan kar raha hun jo kuchh Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen bataya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine Hiraa main eik maah khilwat ikhtiyar ki, jab maine apni khilwat puri kar li, to main nichey utar aaya, mujhey aawaz di gaee, maine apney daain dekha to mujhey koi chiz nazar na aai , maine apney baain dekha to mujhey kuchh nazar na aaya, maine apney peechhey dekha to maine koi chiz na dekhi , maine ooper dekha to maine koi chiz na dekhi , phir main Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aa gaya to maine kaha : mujhey chadar odha do, unhoney mujhey chadar odha di, aur unhoney mujh par thanda pani dala, aur phir mujh par ye aayaat nazil hui. (jis ka tarjama is tarah hai) ''aey chadar odhney waley ! khadey ho jaeyn , aur daraeyn, aur apney rab ki badai bayan karen, aur apney kapdon ko paak saaf rakhen aur shirk se kinara kushi ikhtiyar keren.'' aur ye Namaz farz honey se pehley ka waqia hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5852,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas Jibrael (Alaihissalam) tashrif laye, aap us waqt bachchon ke sath khel rahey they, unhoney aap ko pakad kar litaya , aap ka Sina chaak karkey dil se khoon ka eik loathra nikal kar farmaya : ye aap ke (jism mein) shetan ka hissa tha, phir us (dil) ko soney ki eik tasht mein (rakh kar) aab zam-zam se dhoya aur phir usey jod kar uski jagah par dobara rakh diya, ye (maajra dekh kar) bachchey daud kar aap ki walida yani aap ki daaya ke paas aaye aur unhoney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qatl kar diya gaya hai. wo fauran aap ke paas pahunchiy to dekha ke aap ka rang tabdeel ho chuka tha, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya , maine silaai ka nishan aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke seene Mubarak par dekha tha. rawahu Muslim."
5853,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Makka mein us patthar ko pehchanta hun jo ke meri bea'sat (paighambari) se qabl mujhey salam kiya karta tha, aur main usey ab-bhi pehchanta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
5854,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Makka walon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mutalba kiya ke wo unhen koi mojza dikhayen , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen chaand ke do tukdey hotey huey dikhaya, yahan tak ke unhoney Hiraa ko un do tukdon ke darmiyan dekha. muttafaq aleh."
5855,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein chaand ke do tukdey huey they, eik tukda pahad ke ooper aur eik tukda uskey nichey (gira) tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(meri nabuwat ki) gawahi do.'' (doosra maani) : ''(mojza) dekh lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
5856,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Jahal ne kaha : kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumharey samney apna chehra khaak aalud (yani sajda) kartey hain? unhoney kaha : haan , usney kaha : laat aur uzza ki qism ! agar maine usey aisey kartey huey dekha to main uski gardan par apna paaon rakhunga, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur Namaz shuru kar di Abu-Jahal ne us doran aap ki gardan par paaon rakhney ka irada kiya, wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par hamla karney ke liye aagey badha lekin wo fauran ultey paaon dauda aur khud ko apney dono haathon se bachaney laga , us se puchha gaya, tujhey kya hua? usney kaha : merey aur us (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ke darmiyan aag ki khandaq, heybiyat aur (farishton ke) par hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo merey qarib aa jata to farishtey usey uchak letey aur uska jod-jod tod detey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5857,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke eik aadmi aap ke paas aaya to usney faaqey ki shikayat ki, phir doosra shakhs aaya aur usney rahzani ki shikayat ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Adi !kya to ne haira dekha hai? agar teri umr daraz hui to tum dekhogey aurat haira (kufey ke paas eik basti) se hodaj mein Sawar ho kar aaeygi aur wo Kaba ka tawaf karegi, usey us doran Allah ke siwa kisi ka dar khof nahin hoga. agar tumhari zindagi daraz hui to tum par kisraa ke khazaney khol diye jaeyngey, aur agar tum kuchh aur dino tak zinda rahey to tum dekhogey ke aadmi haath mein sona ya chaandi lekar aisey aadmi ki talash mein nikley-ga jo usey qubul kar ley lekin usey aisa koi aadmi nahin milega jo usey qubul kar ley , aur tum mein se her eik qiyamat ke din Allah se mulaqat kerega ke us waqt Allah Taala aur bandey ke darmiyan koi tarjamaan nahin hoga jo ke uski tarjamaani kar sakey, wo farmaeyga : kya maine teri taraf Rasool nahin bhejey they ke wo teri taraf mera pegham pahunchaey? wo shakhs kahega , kyon nahin zarur aaye they, Allah Taala farmaeyga : kya maine tujhey maal nahin diya tha aur maine tujhey fazilat ata nahin ki thi? wo arz kerega : kyon nahin, zarur ata ki thi, wo apney daain dekhega to usey jahannam nazar aaeygi , phir wo apney baain dekhega to usey jahannam nazar aaeygi. jahannam se bach jaao, chahey (chaahe) khajoor ka eik tukda hi ho, chunanche jo shakhs ye bhi na paey to wo achhi baat ke zariey (aag se bach jaey).'' Adi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine hodaj mein sawar aurat ko dekha ke wo haira se aai aur usney Kaba ka tawaf kiya, aur usey Allah ke siwa kisi aur ka dar khof nahin tha, aur jin ke liye Kisraa bin Hurmuz ke khazaney kholey gaey mein bhi un mein mojud tha, aur agar tumhari umr daraz hui to tum wo kuchh zarur dekhogey, jiski Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne paishangoi farmaee thi ke  ''eik shakhs apney haath mein sona aur chaandi lekar nikley ga.'' Bukhari."
5858,"Hazrat Khabbab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se (kuffar ki eza (takleef) rasaani ki) shikayat ki, aap us waqt Kaba ke saye mein dhaari daar chadar ka sarhana banaey tashrif farma they, hamein mushrekin se bahut takleef pahunch chuki thi, ham ne arz kiya, kya aap Allah se dua nahin farmatey? aap uth kar beth gaey aur aap ka chehra Mubarak surkh ho gaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum se pehley aisey log bhi they ke un mein se kisi ke liye zamin mein gadha khod diya jata aur phir aaraa laya jata aur uskey sar par rakh diya jata, aur uskey do tukdey kar diye jatey , ye chiz bhi usey uskey Deen se nahin rokti thi. lohey ke kanghey unke gosht haddiyon aur putthon mein dhansa diye jatey aur ye chiz bhi unhen unke Deen se nahin rokti thi, Allah ki qism ! ye Deen mukammal hoga yahan tak ke sawar san'aa se Hazare-maut tak safar kareyga aur usey sirf Allah hi ka khof hoga, aur usey apni bakriyon ke mutalliq bhediye ka khof bhi nahin hoga, lekin tum log jaldi kartey ho.'' Bukhari."
5859,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya (biwi) Umme-Haram binte Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif ley jaya kartey they, eik roz aap unke yahan tashrif ley gaey to unhoney aap ko khana khilaya , phir beth kar aap ke sar Mubarak se juein dekhney lagin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so gaey phir (jab) uthey to aap hans rahey they, wo bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap kyon hans rahey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat se kuchh log Allah ki raah mein jihad kartey huey mujhey dikhaye gaey, wo us samandar mein sawar is tarah ja rahey hain jis tarah badshah takht par hotey hain ya wo baadshaahon ki tarah takhton par biraajmaan they.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah se dua karen ke wo mujhey bhi unhi mein se kar dey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmaee, phir aap apna sar rakh kar so gaey, phir bedaar huey to aap hans rahey they, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap kyon hans rahey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ki raah mein jihad kartey huey mujhey dikhaye gaey.'' jaisa ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pehli baar farmaya tha. maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah se dua farmaain ke wo mujhey un mein se kar dey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aap awwaleen mein se hain.'' Umme-Haram (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein bahri (samundri) safar kiya, jab wo samandar se bahar niklen to wo apni sawari se gir kar wafat pa gaeen. muttafaq aleh."
5860,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Zamaad Makka aaya aur wo qabila azdishnuaa se tha, aur wo aaseb waghera ka mantra janta tha usney Makkey ke nadanon se suna ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) majnun hain, usney kaha : agar main us aadmi ko dekhun (aur uska ilaj karun) to shayad Allah merey haathon usey shifa ata farma dey, raawi bayan kartey hain, wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mila aur usney kaha : Muhammad ! main aaseb waghera ka mantra janta hun kya aap ko ilaj ki raghbat hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : (إن الحمد للہ . . . . . عبدہ و رسولہ) ''be-shak her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai, ham uski hamd bayan kartey hain aur usi se madad chahtey hain, jis ko Allah hidayat ata farma dey usey koi gumrah nahin kar sakta, jis ko wo gumrah kar dey usey koi hidayat nahin dey sakta, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' Amaa-baad ! usney arz kiya, yehi kalimaat mujhey dobara sunaeyn chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen martaba ye kalimaat usey sunaiye , to usney arz kya, maine kaahinon saahiron aur shaairon ka kaliam suna hai, lekin maine aap ke kalimaat jaisa koi kaliam nahin suna, ye to intehai behatireen aur baleegh kalimaat hain, apna daste-mubarak laeyn, main Islam par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat karta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se baiat li. rawahu Muslim. Masaabeh ke baaz nuskhon mein (ناعوس البحر) ke alfaz hain, aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ( یھلک الکسریٰ (aur dusri : ( لتفتحن عصابۃ ( ""باب الملاحم"" mein zikr ki gaee hai."
5861,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Sufiyaan bin Harab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bila wastey hadees bayan ki, unhoney farmaya : maine us muddat ke doran jo ke merey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darmiyan (suleh Hudebiya ka ( muahida hua tha, safar kiya, wo bayan kartey hain, main us waqt Sham hi mein tha jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khat Hiraql ko wusul hua, aur unhoney farmaya : Dahiya Kalbi ye khat lekar aaye they, unhoney usey Ameer Basri ko diya aur usney usey Hiraql ke hawaley kiya, Hiraql ne kaha : kya us shakhs ki qom ka koi fard yahan mojud hai jo khud ko Allah ka Rasool khayal karta hai unhoney kaha : ji haan , mujhey bulaya gaya, merey sath kuchh Quraishi bhi they, ham Hiraql ke paas pahunchey to hamein uskey samney bitha diya gaya, usney puchha : ye shakhs jo apney aap ko Nabi samajhta hai, aap mein uska sab se ziyada qaribi rishte-dar kon hai? Abu-Sufiyaan kehtey hain, maine kaha : main , unhoney mujhey uskey samney bithaya aur merey sathiyon ko merey peechhey bitha diya, phir usney apney tarjamaan ko bulaya , aur kaha : un se keh do ke main us (Abu-Sufiyaan) se us shakhs ke mutalliq , jo chand sawalat karunga jisney nabuwat ka daawa kiya hai, agar ye mujh se jhoot boley to tum usey jhutla dena, Abu-Sufiyaan bayan kartey hain, Allah ki qism ! agar jhoot bolney ki bdnaami ka andesha na hota to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq zarur jhoot boltaa, phir usney apney tarjamaan se kaha is se poochho , uska hasab aur nasab kaisa hai? wo kehtey hain maine kaha, wo ham mein nihayat umda hasab aur nasab waley hain, usney kaha : kya unke baap aur daada mein se koi badshah guzra hai? maine kaha : nahin, usney kaha : kya usney tum se is baat se pehley jo ab wo kehta hai koi aisi baat kahi jis par tum ne usey jhoota kaha ho? maine kaha : nahin, usney kaha : uskey perokar kon hain, badey log ya kamzor log? wo kehtey hain, maine kaha : balke kamzor log, usney kaha : kya wo ziyada ho rahey hain ya kam? wo kehtey hain, maine kaha : nahin, balke wo ziyada ho rahey hain, usney kaha : kya is Deen mein dakhil honey ke baad koi shakhs usey bura khayal karkey us se munharif hua (palta) hai? wo kehtey hain, maine kaha : nahin, usney puchha : kya tum ne us se jang ki hai? maine kaha : haan , usney kaha : tumhari us se jang kaisi rahi? wo kehtey hain, maine kaha : jang ham dono ke darmiyan barabar hai, kabhi usey hamari taraf se ruk pahunchti hai aur kabhi hamein uski taraf se ruk pahunchti hai, usney kaha : kya wo bad ehadi bhi karta hai? maine kaha : nahin, albatta ham us waqt uskey sath suleh ki muddat guzar rahey hain, malum nahin wo is mein kya kerega. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! us jumley ke ilawa mujhey aur kahin koi baat dakhil karney ka moqey na mila , usney puchha : kya ye baat us se pehley bhi kisi ne ki thi? maine kaha : nahin, phir usney apney tarjamaan se kaha : usey kaho , maine tujh se uskey hasab aur nasab ke mutalliq puchha to tum ne kaha : wo tum mein sab se ziyada umda hasab aur nasab wala hai, aur Rasool aisey hi hotey hain, unhen unki qom ke unchey hasab aur nasab mein mab-us kiya (bheja) jata hai, maine tujh se sawal kiya, kya uskey baap aur daada mein koi badshah tha? tune kaha : nahin, agar uskey baap aur daada mein se koi badshah hota to main khayal karta ke wo baap aur daada ki badshahat ka talab-gaar hai, maine tujh se uskey man'ne walon ke mutalliq puchha : kya wo zaeef log hain ya badey log hain, to ne kaha : balke wo kamzor log hain, aur Rasulon ke perokar aisey hi hotey hain, maine tujh se puchha : kya usney jo baat ki hai uskey kehney se pehley tum usey jhoot se muttahim (jis par jhoot waghaira ka ilzaam laga ho) kartey they, to ne kaha : nahin, maine pehchan liya ke agar wo logon par jhoot nahin boltaa to phir wo Allah par kaisey jhoot bol sakta hai? maine tujh se sawal kiya : kya uskey Deen mein dakhil honey ke baad koi shakhs usey bura khayal kartey huey murtad bhi hua hai? to ne kaha : nahin, aur eman ki yehi haalat hoti hai ke jab uski bashaashat (farhat aur lazzat) dilon mein raasikh ho jati hai to phir wo nikalta nahin, maine tujh se puchha : kya wo ziyada ho rahey hain ya kam? to ne kaha, wo ziyada ho rahey hain, aur eman isi tarah hota hai yahan tak ke wo mukammal ho jata hai, maine tujh se puchha : kya tum ne us se jang ki hai? tune bataya ke tum ne us se jang ki hai aur jang tumharey darmiyan barabar rahi , Rasulon ka maamla isi tarah hota hai ke un par daure-aazmaish aata hai aur anjam ba-khair unhi ka hota hai, maine tujh se puchha : kya wo bad ehadi karta hai? tune kaha : nahin, aur Rasulon ki yehi shaan hai? wo bad ehadi nahin kartey, maine tujh se sawal kiya : kya aisi baat us se pehley bhi kisi ne ki hai? tune kaha : nahin, agar us se pehley aisi baat kisi ne ki hoti to main khayal karta ke ye aadmi wesi hi baat kar raha hai jo us se pehley ki gaee hai. raawi bayan kartey hain, phir usney puchha : wo tumhen kis chiz ka hukm deta hai? ham ne kaha : wo hamein Namaz padhney , Zakat deney , sila rehmi karney aur paak damani ka hukm deta hai, usney kaha : tum ne jo kuchh kaha hai agar to wo sahih hai to phir wo Nabi hain, mujhey ye to pata tha ke unka zuhoor honey wala hai, lekin mera ye khayal nahin tha ke wo tum mein se hongey, agar mujhey yaqin hota ke main un tak pahunch sakoonga to main un se mulaqat ka sharf hasil karna pasand karta, aur agar main unke paas hota to main unke paaon dhota , aur unki badshahat merey in dono qadmon ki jagah tak pahunch jaeygi, phir usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khat Mubarak mangaa kar padha. ""muttafaq aleh"" aur ye mukammal hadees (باب الکتاب الی الکفار) mein guzar chuki hai."
5862,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) Anas bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Maalik bin Sasaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shabb Mairaj ke mutalliq unhen bataya ke ''main hateem mein letaa hua tha, aur baaz riwayaat mein hai, main Hajar mein letaa hua tha, ke achcha eik aaney wala merey paas aaya to usney mera Sina chaak kiya, merey dil ko nikala , phir merey paas eman se bhara hua soney ka eik tasht laya gaya, merey dil ko dhoya gaya, phir usey bhar diya gaya, phir usey wapis uski jagah par rakh diya gaya.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''phir (merey) pet ko aab zam zam se dhoya gaya, phir usey eman aur hikmat se bhar diya gaya, phir khachchar se chhoti aur gadhey se badi safed rang ki burraaq naami eik sawari merey paas laee gaee , wo apni intihaaye nazar tak apna qadam rakhti thi, mujhey is par Sawar kiya gaya, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) mujhey sath ley chaley , yahan tak ke wo aasmane duniya par pahunchey to unhoney darwaza kholney ke liye kaha, un se puchha gaya, aap kon hain? unhoney farmaya : Jibrael , puchha gaya : aur aap ke sath kon hain? unhoney farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), puchha gaya, kya unhen bulaya gaya hai? unhoney farmaya : haan , kaha gaya : khush aamadeed , aur tashrif laney waley kitney hi achchhey hain, darwaza khol diya gaya, jab main wahan pahuncha to maine wahan Adam (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne bataya : ye aap ke walid Adam (Alaihissalam) hain, unhen salam karen, maine unhen salam kiya aur unhoney salam ka jawab diya, phir unhoney farmaya : Saleh bete ! aur Saleh Nabi khush aamadeed , phir Jibrael (Alaihissalam) mujhey ooper ley gaey yahan tak ke wo doosrey aasman par pahunch gaey, unhoney darwaza kholney ke liye kaha, puchha gaya : kon hai? unhoney farmaya : Jibrael (Alaihissalam) , puchha gaya, aap ke sath kon hai? unhoney kaha : Muhammad ! puchha gaya, kya unki taraf kisi ko bheja gaya tha? farmaya : haan , kaha gaya : khush aamadeed ! aaney waley kitney hi achchhey hain, darwaza khol diya gaya, jab main wahan pahuncha to Yahya aur Esa (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat ho gaee , aur wo dono khaala zaad they. farmaya : ye Yahya (Alaihissalam) hain aur ye Esa (Alaihissalam) hain, un dono ko salam karen, maine salam kiya, to un dono ne salam ka jawab diya, phir farmaya : Saleh bhai ! khush aamadeed , Nabi Saleh khush aamadeed , phir mujhey teesrey aasman ki taraf ley jaya gaya, unhoney darwaza kholney ke liye kaha, puchha gaya, kon hai? farmaya : Jibrael , kaha gaya : aap ke sath kon hai? farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) puchha gaya, kya unki taraf kisi ko bheja gaya tha? farmaya : haan , kaha gaya : khush aamadeed , aaney waley kya hi achchhey hain, darwaza khol diya gaya, jab main udhar pahuncha to wahan Yusuf (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui, unhoney bataya , ye Yusuf (Alaihissalam) hain, unhen salam karen, maine unhen salam kiya to unhoney salam ka jawab diya, phir farmaya : Saleh bhai aur Saleh Nabi khush aamadeed , phir mujhey ooper ley jaya gaya, yahan tak ke chauthey aasman par pahunchey , phir darwaza kholney ke liye darkhast ki, puchha kon hai? kaha : Jibrael , puchha gaya : aap ke sath kon hain? farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , puchha gaya : kya unki taraf bheja gaya tha? farmaya : haan ! kaha gaya : khush aamadeed , aaney waley kitney hi achchhey hain, jab main wahan pahuncha to Idrees (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui, to unhoney kaha, ye Idrees (Alaihissalam) hain, unhen salam karen, maine salam kiya to unhoney salam ka jawab diya phir farmaya : Saleh Nabi khush aamadeed , phir mujhey ooper ley jaya gaya yahan tak ke wo paanchwen aasman par pahunchey aur unhoney darwaza kholney ki darkhast ki to un se puchha gaya, aap kon hain? kaha : Jibrael , puchha gaya, aap ke sath kon hain? farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , puchha gaya, kya unki taraf pegham bheja gaya tha? unhoney farmaya : haan , phir kaha gaya : khush aamadeed , aaney waley kitney hi achchhey hain, jab main wahan pahuncha to wahan Harun (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui farmaya : ye Harun (Alaihissalam) hain unhen salam karen, isliye maine unhen salam kiya, to unhoney salam ka jawab diya, phir farmaya : Saleh bhai , aur Nabi Saleh khush aamadeed , phir wo mujhey aur ooper ley gaey, yahan tak ke ham chatey aasman par pahunchey to unhoney darwaza kholney ke liye kaha, unhoney puchha : kon hain? farmaya : Jibrael , puchha gaya, aap ke sath kon hai? farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , puchha gaya, kya unki taraf pegham bheja gaya tha? farmaya : haan , kaha gaya, khush aamadeed , aaney waley kitney hi achchhey hain, darwaza khol diya gaya, jab main wahan pahuncha to wahan Musa (Alaihissalam) tashrif farma they, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : ye Musa hain, unhen salam karen, maine unhen salam kiya, to unhoney salam ka jawab diya, phir farmaya : Saleh bhai aur Saleh Nabi khush aamadeed jab main un se aagey badhney laga to wo roney lagey , un se puchha gaya : aap kyon ro rahey hain? unhoney farmaya : main isliye rotaa hun ke eik nojawan merey baad mab-us kya (bheja) gaya, aur uski ummat ke jannat mein janey waley afrad , meri ummat ke jannat mein janey waley afrad se ziyada hongey, phir mujhey saatwen aasman par ley jaya gaya, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne darwaza kholney ki darkhast ki, to puchha gaya : aap kon hain? farmaya : Jibrael , puchha gaya, aap ke sath kon hain? farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), puchha gaya, kya unki taraf pegham bheja gaya tha? farmaya : haan , kaha gaya : khush aamadeed , kitney hi achchhey hain aaney waley? jab main wahan pahuncha to wahan Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) tashrif farma they, Jibrael ne farmaya , ye tumharey baap Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) hain, unhen salam karen, chunanche maine unhen salam kiya to unhoney salam ka jawab diya, phir farmaya : Saleh bete aur Saleh Nabi khush aamadeed , phir mujhey sidratul-muntaha tak ley jaya gaya, uskey mewey (bair) Hajar ke matkon ki tarah they, uskey pattey haathi ke kanon ki tarah they, unhoney bataya , ye sidratul-muntaha hai, wahan chaar nehren thin : do andar thin aur do zahiri thin maine kaha : Jibrael ! ye do chizen kya hain, unhoney farmaya : do anduruni nehren , ye do nehren jannat mein behti hain, aur do zahiri nehren , aur ye neel aur faraat hain, phir mujhey baitul-maamur ki taraf ley jaya gaya, phir merey paas sharab, doodh aur shehad ka bartan laya gaya, maine doodh wala bartan utha liya, unhoney farmaya : ye wo fitrat hai jis par aap aur aap ki ummat hai, phir mujh par din mein pachas namazein farz ki gaeen, main wapis aaya aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra to unhoney puchha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kya hukm mila hai? maine kaha : mujhey her roz pachas namazein padhney ka hukm diya gaya hai, unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat her roz pachas namazein padhney ki taqat nahin rakheygi , Allah ki qism ! main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se pehley logon ka tajarba kar chuka hun, aur Bani-Israel ka mujhey sakht tajarba ho chuka hai, aap apney rab ke paas dobara jaeyn aur apni ummat ke liye kami ki darkhast karen, main dobara gaya to mujh se das kam kar di gaeen, phir main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya, unhoney phir wohi baat ki, main phir hazire-khidmat hua, Allah Taala ne phir das namazon ki kami farma di, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas wapis aaya to unhoney phir wohi baat kahi, main phir hazire-khidmat hua, Allah Taala ne das namazein kam kar den, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas wapis aaya to unhoney phir wohi baat dohrani, main phir Allah ke paas gaya to mujh se das kam kar di gaeen, aur mujhey her roz das namazein padhney ka hukm diya gaya, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to unhoney phir wesey hi farmaya , main phir (rab ke huzur) gaya to mujhey her roz paanch namazein padhney ka hukm diya gaya, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to unhoney puchha : aap ko kya hukm diya gaya hai? maine kaha : mujhey her roz paanch namazein padhney ka hukm diya gaya hai, unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat her roz paanch namazein padhney ki taqat nahin rakheygi , kyonkey main aap se pehley logon ka tajarba kar chuka hun aur Bani-Israel ka mujhey sakht tajarba ho chuka hai, aap apney rab ke paas phir jaeyn aur apni ummat ke liye kami ki darkhast karen, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apney rab se (kami Namaz ke liye itni martaba) sawal kya hai lihaza ab mujhey haya aati hai, ab main razi hon aur taslim karta hun, farmaya : jab main wahan se chala to aawaz deney waley ne aawaz di, maine (paanch namazon ka ( apna fariza jari kar diya aur apney bandon par kami farma di.'' muttafaq aleh."
5863,"Hazrat Sabit Bunani (Raziallahu anhu) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas burraaq laee gaee, wo safed lamba chaupaaya tha, jo gadhey se bada aur khachchar se chhota tha, wo apna qadam wahan rakhta tha jahan tak uski nazar jati thi, main is par Sawar hua , aur baitul-Maqdis pahuncha wahan maine usey us halqey (kundey) ke sath baandh diya jiskey sath Anbiya (Alaihissalam) apni sawariyan baandha kartey they.'' farmaya : ''phir main masjid mein dakhil hua to wahan do rakatein padhin, phir wahan se nikla to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey paas eik bartan sharab aur eik bartan doodh ka laye to maine doodh ka bartan muntakhab kiya, is par Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : aapney fitrat ka intikhaab farmaya hai, phir hamein aasman ki taraf ley jaya gaya.'' uskey baad raawi ne hadees saabiq ke ham-maani riwayat bayan ki, farmaya : ''main Adam (Alaihissalam) se mila to unhoney mujhey khush aamadeed kaha, aur merey liye khair aur barkat ki dua farmaee.'' aur farmaya : '' teesrey aasman par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui, unki shaan ye hai ke unhen nisf (aadha) Husan ata kiya gaya hai, unhoney bhi mujhey khush aamadeed kaha, aur duaaey khair farmaee.'' us riwayat mein raawi ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ke roney ka zikr nahin kiya, aur farmaya : ''saatwen aasman par Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui, aap baitul-maamur se tek lagaey huey they, wahan her roz sattar hazar farishtey dakhil hotey hain aur phir dobara unki baari nahin aati, phir mujhey sidratul-muntaha ley jaya gaya, uskey pattey haathi ke kanon ki tarah they, jabkey uska phal matkon ki tarah tha, jab usko Allah ke hukm se jis chiz ne dhapna tha dhanp liya, to uski haalat badal gaee , Allah ki makhluq mein se uskey Husan ki koi tareef bayan nahin kar sakta , chunanche usney meri taraf jo ""wahi"" kerni thi, wo kar di, aur din raat mein mujh par pachas namazein farz kar di gaeen, main (ye hukm lekar) Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to unhoney farmaya : aap ke rab ne aap ki ummat par kya farz kiya hai? maine kaha : her roz pachas namaazein, unhoney farmaya : apney rab ke paas dobara jaeyn aur us se kami ki darkhast karen kyonkey aap ki ummat uski taqat nahin rakheygi , kyonkey main Bani-Israel ko aazamaa chuka hun aur unka tajarba kar chuka hun.'' farmaya : ''main apney rab ke paas gaya, to arz kiya, rab ji ! meri ummat par kami farmaeyn, mujh se paanch namazein kam kar di gaeen, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas wapis aaya to unhen bataya ke mujh se paanch namazein kam kar di gaeen hain, unhoney farmaya : aap ki ummat iski taqat nahin rakhti , aap apney rab ke paas jaeyn aur us se kami ki darkhast keren.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main apney rab aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ke darmiyan aata jata raha yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne farmaya : Muhammad ! her roz ye paanch namazein hain, aur her Namaz ke liye das guna ajr hai, is tarah ye pachas namazein huin , jo shakhs kisi neki ka irada karey aur wo usey na kar sakey to uskey liye eik neki likh di jati hai, aur agar wo us neki ko kar ley to uskey liye das nekiyan likh di jati hain, aur jo shakhs kisi burai ka irada karta hai lekin wo us burai ka irtikab nahin karta to uskey liye kuchh bhi nahin likha jata, aur agar wo uska irtikab kar leta hai to uskey liye eik hi burai likhi jati hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main nichey aaya yahan tak ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aa kar unhen bataya to unhoney phir bhi yehi farmaya : apney rab ke paas jaeyn aur us se kami ki darkhast keren.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine kaha : main itni baar apney rab ke paas gaya hun lihaza ab mujhey (us kami ki darkhast kartey huey) haya aati hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5864,"Hazrat ibne-Shahab, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain unhoney kaha : Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) hadees bayan kiya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Makka mein tha ke merey ghar ki chhat khol di gaee to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) nazil huey unhoney mera Sina chaak kiya, phir usey aab zam zam ke sath dhoya , phir wo hikmat aur eman se bhari hui soney ki tasht laye, usey merey seeney mein dal diya, phir usey jod diya, phir mera haath pakda aur mujhey aasman ki taraf ley gaey, jab main aasmane duniya par pahuncha to Jibrael ne aasman ke muhafiz se kaha, darwaza kholo , usney puchha : aap kon hain? farmaya , Jibrael , usney puchha : aap ke sath koi hai? unhoney farmaya : haan , merey sath Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. usney puchha : kya unki taraf bulaney ke liye bheja gaya tha? unhoney farmaya : haan , jab darwaza khol diya gaya to ham aasmane duniya par chaley gaey, wahan eik aadmi betha hua tha kuchh log uskey daain taraf they aur kuchh uskey baain taraf , jab wo apni daain janib dekhtey to muskura detey aur jab apni baain janib dekhtey to ronaa shuru kar detey , unhoney kaha : khush aamadeed Nabi Saleh aur bete saleh, maine Jibrael (Alaihissalam) se puchha ye kon hain? unhoney farmaya : ye Adam (Alaihissalam) hain, aur unke daain aur baain janib jo giroh hain, ye unki aulad ki roohen hain, unke daain taraf wala giroh ehale jannat ka hai, aur unke baain taraf wala giroh jahannamiyon ka hai, jab wo apni daain janib dekhtey hain to muskuraatey hain, aur jab apni baain janib dekhtey hain to ro detey hain, phir mujhey doosrey aasman tak ley jaya gaya, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne uskey muhafiz se kaha : darwaza kholo , uskey muhafiz ne bhi unhen wesay hi kaha jaisa pehley aasman waley muhafiz ne kaha tha.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zikr farmaya ke unhoney aasmano mein Adam, Idrees, Musa, Esa aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat ki, aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bayan nahin kiya ke unki manaazil kaisi hain, albatta unhoney ye zikr kiya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko aasmane duniya par aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko chatey aasman par paya , ibne-Shahab ne bayan kiya, ibne Hazam ne mujhey khabar di ke ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hiba Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) dono bayan kiya kartey they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir mujhey ooper ley jaya gaya yahan tak ke main is qadr buland jagah par pahunch gaya ke main qalmon ke likhney ki aawaz sunta tha.'' ibne Hazam aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne meri ummat par pachas namazein farz kin, mein ye (hukm) lekar wapis hua , aur mera guzar Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se hua to unhoney farmaya : Allah ne aap ki ummat par kya farz kiya hai? maine kaha : pachas namazein , unhoney farmaya : apney rab ke paas wapis jaeyn kyonkey aap ki ummat taqat nahin rakheygi , unhoney mujhey wapis lota diya, to Allah Taala ne un (namazon) ka kuchh hissey kam kar diya, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas wapis aaya to maine bataya ke usney un mein se kuchh kam kar di hain, unhoney farmaya : apney rab ke paas wapis jaeyn kyonkey aap ki ummat iski taqat nahin rakh sakeygi, main wapis gaya aur apni baat dohrani to usney un mein se kuch aur kam kar den, main phir unke paas wapis aaya, to unhoney farmaya : apney rab ke paas wapis jaeyn kyonkey aap ki ummat iski taqat nahin rakheygi, maine phir us se darkhast ki to usney farmaya : wo (adaegi mein) paanch hain aur (sawab mein) wo pachas hain merey yahan baat tabdeel nahin ki jati, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to unhoney farmaya : apney rab ke paas phir jaeyn, maine kaha : mujhey apney rab ke (paas bar-bar janey) se sharam aati hai, phir mujhey sidratul-muntaha tak ley jaya gaya, kaee rangon ne usey dhanp rakha tha, main nahin janta wo kya hain? phir mujhey jannat mein ley jaya gaya, wahan motiyon ke gumbad they aur uski mitti kastoori ki thi.'' muttafaq aleh."
5865,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Mairaj karaai gaee to unhen sidratul-muntaha tak ley jaya gaya, wo chatey aasman par hai, zamin se ooper janey wali her chiz ki had yahan tak hai, usi maqam se ehkamaat liye jatey hain aur ooper se jo hukm aata hai wo yahin aa kar rukta hai, aur phir yahan se ehkam liye jatey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis chiz ne sidra ko dhanpana tha usney usey dhanp rakha tha.'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya us se murad ye hai ke wo soney ke parwane aur patingey they. farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen chizen ata ki gaeen, aap ko paanch namazein ata ki gaeen, sura Baqra ki aakhiri aayaat aur aap ki ummat mein se jo shakhs Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek thehraney jaisey kabeera gunah nahin kerega usko bakhsh diya jaeyga. rawahu Muslim."
5866,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine apney aap ko Hajar (hateem) mein (khadey huey) dekha, jabkey Quraish mujh se merey safar Mairaj ke mutalliq sawal kar rahey they, unhoney baitul-Maqdis ki kuchh chizon ke mutalliq mujh se sawalat kiye lekin mujhey wo yad nahin tha, main is qadr ghamgin hua ke is tarah ka gham mujhey kabhi nahin hua tha, chunanche Allah ne usey meri nazron ke samney buland kar diya mein usey dekh raha tha, isliye wo mujh se jis bhi chiz ke mutalliq sawal kartey to main unhen bata deta tha, maine apney aap ko Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki jamaat mein dekha, maine achcha Musa (Alaihissalam) ko haalate-qiyam mein Namaz padhtey huey dekha, unka qad darmiyaanaa hai aur baal ghunghriyaaley hain, goya wo Shanoo qabiley ke aadmi hain, phir maine Esa (Alaihissalam) ko khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey huey dekha, Urwa bin Masood Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) ki un se bahut ziyada mushaabihat hai, aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) bhi khadey Namaz padh rahey hain, main un se sab se ziyada mushaabihat rakhta hun, Namaz ka waqt hua to maine unki imaamat karaai, chunanche jab main Namaz se farigh hua to kisi kehney waley ne mujhey kaha : Muhammad ! ye jahannam ka darogha Maalik hai, aap usey salam karen, maine uski taraf tawajjoh ki to usney mujhey salam mein pehal ki.'' rawahu Muslim."
5867,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab Quraish ne (waqia Mairaj ke mutalliq) mujhey jhutlaya to main hateem mein khada ho gaya, Allah ne merey liye baitul-Maqdis ko roshan kar diya, chunanche maine usey dekh kar uski alaamaat bayan karni shuru kar din.'' muttafaq aleh."
5868,"Hazrat Anas bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ham ghaar mein they, maine sar uthaya to dekha ke mushrekin ke paaon nazar aa rahey they goya wo hamarey saron par hon, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! agar un mein se koi apney paaon ki taraf nazar kar ley to wo hamein dekh lega , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! aisey do aadmiyon ke barey main tumhara kya khayal hai, jinkey sath teesra Allah hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5869,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid (Aazib (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Abu-Bakar ! jab aap raat ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath (hijrat ke liye) rawana huey to aap ka ye safar kaisey guzra? unhoney farmaya : ham raat bhar aur agley roz do-pehar tak chaltey rahey, raasta khaali tha wahan se koi bhi nahin guzar raha tha, hamein eik taweel chattan nazar aai jis ka saya tha, abhi wahan dhoop nahin aai thi, ham ne wahan qiyam kiya, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aaram ke liye apney haathon se jagah barabar ki is par eik posteen bichhaai, aur phir maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap so jaeyn , aur main ird-gird ke halaat ka jayeza leta hun, aap so gaey aur main jayeza leney ke liye bahar nikal aaya, maine eik charwaahaa aatey huey dekha aur usey kaha : kya teri bakriyan doodh deti hain? usney kaha : haan , maine kaha : kya tum (merey liye) doodh nikalogey? usney kaha : haan , usney eik bakri pakdi aur lakdi ke piyaley mein doodh dohaa, aur merey paas eik bartan tha jisey maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye sath rakha tha, aap us se sairab hotey aur usi se pani peetey aur wuzu kiya kartey they, main doodh lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap ko jagana munasib na samjha , maine intizar kiya yahan tak ke aap bedaar huye, maine doodh par pani dala yahan tak ke uska nichlaa hissey bhi thanda ho gaya, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! nosh farmaeyn, aapney doodh nosh farmaya to mujhey fursat muyassar aai phir aapney farmaya : ''kya kooch karney ka waqt nahin hua?'' maine arz kiya, kyon nahin, ho gaya hai, farmaya ham ne zawal aaftaab ke baad kooch kiya, aur Suraqa bin Malik ne hamara peechha kiya to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! peechha karney wala hamein aa lena chahta hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gham na karo, Allah hamarey sath hai.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye badduaa farmaee to uska ghoda pet tak sakht zamin mein dhans gaya, usney kaha : maine tumhen dekha ke tum ne merey liye badduaa ki hai, tum merey liye dua karo aur main tumhen Allah ki zamanat deta hun ke main tumhari talash mein nikalney walon ko tumharey peechhey nahin aaney dunga, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye dua farmaee to wo najat pa gaya, phir wo jisey bhi milta us se yehi kehta is taraf tumhen janey ki zarurat nahin, mein udhar se ho aaya hun, is tarah wo her milney waley ko wapis kar deta. muttafaq aleh."
5870,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tashrif aawri ke mutalliq suna to wo us waqt phal tod rahey they, wo fauran Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aur arz kiya, main aap se teen sawal karta hun jinhen sirf Nabi hi janta hai, (bataeyn) alaamaat qiyamat mein se sab se pehli nishani kya hai? ehle jannat ka sab se pehla khana kya hoga? bachcha kab apney walid ke mushabeh hota hai aur kab apni walida ke mushabeh hota hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael ne abhi abhi unke mutalliq mujhey bataya hai, jahan tak alaamaat qiyamat ka talluq hai to pehli alamat eik aag hogi jo logon ko mashriq se maghrib ki taraf jama kar deygi, raha jannatiyon ka pehla khana to wo machli ke jigar ka eik kinara hoga, aur jab aadmi ka pani aurat ke pani (mani) par ghalib aa jata hai to bachcha walid ke mushabeh hota hai aur jab aurat ka pani ghalib aa jata hai to bachcha aurat ke mushabeh ho jata hai.'' (ye jawab sun kar) unhoney kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur be-shak aap Allah ke Rasool hain, (phir farmaya) Allah ke Rasool ! Yahudi badey bohtan baaz hain, agar unhen , is se pehley ke aap un se merey mutalliq poochhen, merey Islam qubul karney ka pata chal gaya to wo mujh par bohtan lagaeyngey, chunanche itney mein Yahudi aagey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abdullah ka tumharey yahan kya maqam hai? unhoney bataya ke wo ham mein sab se behtar, ham mein sab se behtar ke bete, hamarey sardar aur hamarey sardar ke bete hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bataao agar Abdullah bin Salam Islam qubul kar lein (to phir)? unhoney kaha, Allah unhen is se panah mein rakhey, Abdullah isi doran bahar tashrif ley aaye aur unhoney kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, phir ye (yahudi unke barey mein) kehney lagey : wo ham mein sab se bura hai aur ham mein se sab se burey ka beta hai, aur wo unki kami nikalne aur tohin karney lagey, Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! yehi wo chiz thi jis ka mujhey andesha tha. Bukhari."
5871,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Abu Sufiyan ki aamad ka hamein pata chala to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mashwara kiya to Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar aap hamein samandar mein kood janey ka hukm farmaeyngey to ham is mein kood jaeyngey, aur agar aap barakil-ghamaad tak janey ka hukm farmaeyngey to ham wahan tak bhi pahuncheingey, raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ko bulaya , phir kooch kiya yahan tak ke Badr ke maqam par padaaw dala, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yahan falan qatl hoga.'' aur aap apney daste-mubarak se zamin par nishan laga rahey they, yahan aur yahan, raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke nishan ki jagah se koi bhi aagey peechey qatl nahin hua tha. rawahu Muslim."
5872,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-Badr ke moqe par apney khemey mein yun dua farmaee : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se terey ehad aur aman aur terey wadey ka sawal karta hun, aey Allah ! kya to chahta hai ke aaj ke baad teri ibadat na ki jaey?'' itney mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ka daste-mubarak pakad liya aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! bas kijiye ! aapney rab se kis qadr israr se dua ki hai, phir aap bahar tashrif laye us waqt aap khub tez chal rahey they aur aapney zireh pehan rakhi thi, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''an-qareeb ye giroh shikast kha jaeyga, aur peeth pher kar bhag jaeyngey.'' (Bukhari)."
5873,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Badr ke roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aalaat Harab sajaaey apney ghodey ki lagaam thaamey huey tashrif la rahey they.'' (Bukhari).
5874,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, us roz eik musalman , eik mushrik ka peecha kar raha tha, uskey aagey us (musalman) ne us (mushrik) ke ooper eik kodey ki aawaz suni, aur ghud sawar ko ye kehtey huey suna : heezom (ghodey ka naam hai) aagey badh, achcha us (musalman) ne mushrik ko apney samney chit gira hua paya aur usney usey dekha ke kodaa padney se uski naak aur uska chehra phat chuka tha aur jahan kodaa pada tha wo jagah kaali ho gaee thi, wo Ansari aaya aur unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se waqia bayan kiya to aapney farmaya : ''tum ne sach kaha, ye teesrey aasman se madad aai thi.'' us din unhoney sattar (kafiron) ko qatl kiya aur sattar ko qaidi banaya. rawahu Muslim."
5875,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine uhad ke roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daain baain do aadmi dekhey un par safed kapdey they aur wo badi shiddat ke sath lad rahey they, maine un dono ko us se pehley dekha tha na baad mein, yani wo Jibrael aur Mekael (Alaihissalam) they. muttafaq aleh."
5876,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chand aadmiyon ko Abu-Raafe (yahudi) ki taraf bheja, Abdullah bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) raat ke waqt uskey ghar mein dakhil ho gaey aur usey qatl kar diya, Abdullah bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine talwaar uskey pet mein utaar di yahan tak ke wo uski pusht tak pahunch gaee , jab mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke maine usey qatl kar diya hai, to main darwazey kholney laga yahan tak ke main aakhiri zeeney tak pahunch gaya, maine apna paaon rakha aur main gir gaya, chaandni raat thi, meri pindli toot gaee, maine amaamey ke sath is par patti baandhi, aur main apney sathiyon ke paas chala aaya phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se pura waqia bayan kiya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apna paaon phailaoo.'' maine apna paaon phelaya to aapney is par apna daste-mubarak phera to wo aisey ho gaya jaisey kabhi is mein takleef hui hi na thi. Bukhari."
5877,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ghazwae-khandaq ke moqe par khandaq khod rahey they to eik bahut sakht chattan nikal aai, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kiya : khandaq mein ye eik chattan nikal aai hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(achchhaa) main utarta hun.'' phir aap khadey huye, us waqt aap ke pet par pathar bandhaa hua tha, teen din guzar chukey they aur ham ne koi chiz chakh kar bhi nahin dekhi thi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kudaal pakad kar maari to wo (chattan) aisi ret ki manind ho gaee jo aasani se girti hai, main apni ehliya (biwi) ke paas aaya to puchha : kya tumharey paas kuchh (khaney ko) hai? kyonkey maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sakht bhook ke aalim mein dekha hai, usney eik thaili nikali us main eik saa jau they aur hamarey paas bakri ka eik bachcha tha, maine usey zibeh kiya, jau pisey yahan tak ke ham ne gosht ko handiya mein rakha, phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur sargoshi ke andaz mein arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham ne apna bakri ka eik bachcha zibeh kiya hai aur eik saa jau ka aataa goondhaa hai, lihaza aap tashrif laeyn aur kuchh sathiyon ko bhi sath ley chalen, lekin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zor se aawaz di : ''khandaq walo ! Jabir ne ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) ka ehtimam kiya hai, aao jaldi karo.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum merey aaney tak apni handiya choolhey se utaarna na roti pakaanaa shuru karna.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to maine aap ke samney aataa nikala , aapney is mein apna luaab milaya aur barkat ki dua ki, phir farmaya : ''roti pakaaney wali ko bulaoo wo tumharey sath roti pakaey aur handiya se salan nikaltey raho, lekin usey choolhey se nichey na utaaro.'' wo eik hazar ki tadaad mein they, main Allah ki qism uthata hun ke un sab ne kha liya yahan tak ke wo bach gaya, aur wo wapis chaley gaey jabkey hamari handiya pehley ki tarah bhari hui thi aur aatey ki rotiyaan pehley ki tarah pakaee ja rahi thin. muttafaq aleh."
5878,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke khandaq khodte waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya , aap us waqt unke sar par haath pher rahey they aur farma rahey they : ''Sumayya ke bete ! tujhey takaaleef ka samna hoga aur tujhey baaghi giroh Shahid karega.'' rawahu Muslim."
5879,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Surad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab giroh mutafarriq (alag-alag) ho gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab ham un par chadhai karengey, wo ham par chadhai na kar sakengey, ab ham unki taraf pesh qadmi karengey.'' Bukhari."
5880,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khandaq se wapis aaye, hathiyar rakh diye aur ghusl farma liya to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aap ke paas tashrif laye, wo apney sar se ghubar jhaad rahey they, unhoney farmaya : ''aapney hathiyar utaar diye hain, Allah ki qism ! maine abhi tak apne jism par pahan rakhey hain, unki taraf chalen.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kahan?'' unhoney Qureza ki taraf ishara farmaya chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki taraf rawana huey. muttafaq aleh."
5881,"Hazrat Sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, goya main bano ghanam ki galiyon mein uthti hui ghubar dekh raha hun jo Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ke sathiyon ki wajeh se ud rahi thi, ye us waqt hua jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) banu Qureza ki taraf chaley they. muttafaq aleh."
5882,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Hudebiya ke moqe par Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ko piyas lagi, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney pani ka eik bartan tha, aapney us se wuzu kiya, phir log aap ki taraf mutawajjeh huye, aur arz kiya, hamarey paas pani nahin jis se ham wuzu kar saken aur pi saken, faqat wohi hai jo aap ki chhaagal mein hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna daste-mubarak chhaagal mein rakha , aur aap ki ungliyon se chashmon ki tarah pani bahney laga , raawi bayan kartey hain, ham ne pani piya aur wuzu kiya, Jabir se puchha gaya, us waqt tumhari tadaad kitni thi? unhoney farmaya : agar ham eik lakh bhi hotey tab bhi wo pani hamein kafi hota, albatta ham us waqt pandarah sau they. muttafaq aleh."
5883,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Hudebiya ke roz ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chaudah so ki tadaad mein they, Hudebiya eik kunwaan tha, ham ne us se sara pani nikal liya tha aur us main eik qatra tak nahin chhoda tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak ye baat pahunchi to aap wahan tashrif laye aur uskey kinarey par beth gaey, phir aapney pani ka eik bartan mangaayaa , wuzu farmaya , phir kulli ki, dua ki, phir usko us (kunwen) mein undel diya, phir farmaya : ''kuchh der isey rehney do.'' chunanche (uskey baad) unhoney khud piya, apney janwaron ko pilaya aur kooch karney tak ye (peeney, pilaney ka ( silsila jari raha. Bukhari."
5884,"Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Rijaa se aur wo Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain unhoney kaha : ham eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, logon ne aap se piyas ki shikayat ki, aap sawari se nichey utrey , aur aapney falan shakhs ko aawaz di, Abu-Rijaa ne us shakhs ka naam liya tha lekin Auf uska naam bhool gaey, aur aapney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bulaya aur farmaya : ''dono jaao aur pani talash karo, wo dono gaey aur pani ki talash shuru ki, wo chaltey gaey yahan tak ke wo eik aurat se miley jo pani ke do mishkeezey apney oont par latkaaey huey aur khud unke darmiyan bethi ja rahi thi, wo dono usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaye, unhoney usko uskey oont se nichey utaar liya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik bartan mangaayaa aur dono mishkeezon ke munh us bartan mein khol diye, aur tamam logon mein aelan kara diya gaya ke khud bhi piyo aur janweron ko bhi pilaao, raawi bayan kartey hain, ham chaalis piyasey aadmiyon ne khub sair ho kar pani piya aur ham ne apney tamam mishkeezey aur bartan bhi bhar liye , Allah ki qism ! jab un se pani lena band kar diya to hamein aisey mehsus ho raha tha ke ab un mein pani pehley se bhi ziyada hai. muttafaq aleh."
5885,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they yahan tak ke ham ne eik wasee (lambi-chaudi) wadi mein padaaw kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazaey-hajat ke liye tashrif ley gaey, aapney oat ke liye koi chiz na dekhi albatta wadi ke kinarey par do darkht dekhey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un mein se eik ki taraf chal diye, aur uski eik shaakh pakad kar farmaya : ''Allah ke hukm se mujh par parda kar.'' chunanche usney nakel diye huey oont ki tarah jhuk kar aap ke ooper parda kiya, jis tarah wo apney qaaid ki itaat karta hai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) doosrey darkht ke paas gaey aur uski eik shaakh ko pakad kar farmaya : ''Allah ke hukm se mujh par parda kar.'' wo bhi isi tarah aap par jhuk gaya, yahan tak ke jab wo dono nisf (aadhe) fasley par pahunch gaey to farmaya : ''Allah ke hukm se mujh par saya kar do.'' chunanche wo dono qarib ho gaey (yahan tak ke aap qazaey-hajat se farigh ho gaey) main betha apney dil mein soch raha tha ke itney mein achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye , aur maine dono darakhton ko dekha ke wo alag alag ho gaey, aur her eik apney taney par khada ho gaya. rawahu Muslim."
5886,"Hazrat Yazid bin Abi Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ki pindli par chot ka nishan dekha to maine kaha : Abu-Muslim ! ye chot kaisi hai? unhoney farmaya : ye chot mujhey ghazwae-khaibar ke moqe par lagi thi, logon ne to keh diya tha : Salma (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid ho gaey, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapney wahan teen baar dam kiya aur phir aaj tak mujhey uski koi shikayat nahin hui. Bukhari."
5887,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zaid, Jaafar aur ibne Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki khabar shahadat aaney se pehley hi unki shahadat ke mutalliq logon ko bata diya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Zaid ne parcham thaam liya aur wo Shahid kar diye gaey, phir Jaafar ne thaam liya wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey phir ibne Rawaha ne thaam liya to wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey.'' us waqt aap ki aakhon se aansu rawan they.'' yahan tak ke Allah ki talwaaron mein se eik talwaar yani Khalid bin Waleed ne parcham thaam liya aur Allah ne unhen Fateh ata farmaee hai.'' Bukhari."
5888,"Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-Hunain ke moqe par main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha, jab musalmanon aur kafiron ka aamna samna hua to kuchh musalman bhag khadey huey jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney khachchar ko kuffar ki taraf bhagaa rahey they aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khachchar ki lagaam thaamey huey tha, main us (khachchar) ko rok raha tha ke wo tez na daudey jabkey Abu-Sufiyaan bin Haris Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki rikaab thaamey huey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abbas ! darkht (ke nichey baiate-rizwaan karney) walon ko aawaz do.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki aawaz buland thi, wo bayan kartey hain, maine apni buland aawaz se kaha : darkht (ke nichey bait karney) waley kahan hain? wo bayan kartey hain, Allah ki qism ! jab unhoney meri aawaz suni to wo is tarah wapis aaye jis tarah gaaey apni aulad ke paas aati hai, unhoney arz kiya, ham hazir hain ! ham hazir hain ! raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney kuffar se qitaal kiya us roz ansaar ka naara ya ansaar tha, raawi bayan kartey hain, phir ye na'ra bano Haris bin Khazraj tak mehdud ho kar reh gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney khachchar par se maidane-jang ki taraf dekha to farmaya : ''ab maidane jang garm ho gaya hai.'' phir aapney kankariyaan pakdin aur unhen kafiron ke chehron par phenka , phir farmaya : ''Muhammad ke rab ki qism ! wo shikast khurda hain.'' Allah ki qism ! unki taraf kankariyaan phenkna hi unki shikast ka baais tha, main unki hiddat (garmi), unki ladaai aur unki talwaaron ko kamzor hi dekhta raha, aur unke mamley ko zaleel hi dekhta raha. rawahu Muslim."
5889,"Hazrat Abu Is'haq bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Abu Imaara ! ghazwa Hunain ke moqe par tum log bhag gaey they? unhoney kaha : nahin, Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nahin phirey they, lekin aap ke Sahaba mein se kuchh nojawan , jinkey paas ziyada aslaha nahin tha, unka samna aisey mahir teer andazon se hua , jin ka koi teer khata nahin jata tha, unhoney un par teer barsaey , wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf aaye . us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney safed khachchar par Sawar they, aur Abu-Sufiyaan bin Haris aap ke aagey they, aap khachchar se nichey utrey aur Allah se madad talab ki, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us waqt farma rahey they : ''main Nabi hun ye jhoot nahin, main Abdul Muttalib ka beta hun.'' phir aapney unki saf bandi farmaee. rawahu Muslim."
5890,"Aur Sahih Bukhari mein usi ke ham-maani hai. aur Saheehain ki riwayat mein hai, Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Allah ki qism ! jab ladaai shiddat ikhtiyar kar jati to ham aap ke zariey bachaaw kartey they aur ham mein se sab se ziyada shujaa' (bahadur) wo tha jo (maidane-jang mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke barabar rehta. muttafaq aleh."
5891,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ghazwae-Hunain mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chand Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) peeth pher gaey, jab wo (kafir) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par hamla aawar huey to aap khachchar se nichey utrey aur zamin se mitti ki mutthi bhari, phir usey unke chehron ki taraf phainktey huey farmaya : ''(unke) chehrey jhulas jaeyn.'' us mutthi se un tamam insanon (kafiron) ki aankhen mitti se bhar gaeen aur wo peeth pher kar bhag gaey, Allah ne unhen shikast se dochaar kar diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se hasil honey wala maale-ghanimat musalmanon mein taqseem farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
5892,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-Hunain mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareek they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aisey shakhs ke barey mein , jo aap ke sath tha aur musalman honey ka daawa karta tha, farmaya : ''ye jahannamiyon mein se hai.'' jab ladaai shuru hui to wo shakhs bahut himmat ke sath ladaa aur bahut ziyada zakhmi ho gaya, eik aadmi aaya aur usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn ke aapney jis shakhs ke barey mein farmaya tha ke wo jahannamiyon mein se hai usney to Allah ki raah mein bahut himmat ke sath ladaai ladi hai aur usney bahut ziyada zakhm khaye hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! wo jahannamiyon mein se hai.'' qarib tha ke baaz log shak aur shubha ka shikar ho jatey, wo aadmi abhi usi kash-m-kash mein tha ke us aadmi ne zakhmon ki takleef mehsus ki aur apney tarkash ki taraf haath badha kar eik teer nikala aur usey apney seeney mein pewast kar liya , musalman ye manzar dekh kar daudtey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur arz kiya Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ne aap ki baat sach kar dikhai, falan shakhs ne apney seeney mein teer pewast karkey khudkushi kar li hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : Allahu-Akbar ! main gawahi deta hun ke main Allah ka banda aur uska Rasool hun, Bilal ! khadey ho kar aelan kar do ke jannat mein sirf momin hi jaeyngey, be-shak Allah apney Deen ki madad faajir shakhs se bhi ley leta hai.'' Bukhari."
5893,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jadu kar diya gaya yahan tak ke aap ko khayal guzarta ke aapney koi kaam kar liya hai halanke aapney usey nahin kiya hota tha, yahan tak ke eik roz aap merey yahan tashrif farma they, aap Allah se bar-bar dua kar rahey they, phir farmaya : ''Aaisha ! kya tumhen malum hai ke maine jis chiz ke barey mein Allah se sawal kiya tha usney wo chiz mujhey de-di hai : do aadmi merey paas aaye , un mein se eik merey sarhaaney beth gaya aur doosra merey paaon ke paas phir un mein se eik ne apney sathi se kaha : unhen kya takleef hai? usney kaha : in par jadu kiya gaya hai, usney puchha : un par kis ne jadu kiya hai? usney kaha : Labid bin Aasam Yahudi ne, usney kaha : kis chiz mein? usney kaha : kanghey aur baalon mein aur nar khajoor ke khoshey mein hai, usney puchha : wo kahan hai? usney kaha : zarwaan ke kunwen mein.'' chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney chand Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath us kunwen par tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : ''ye wo kunwaan hai jo mujhey dikhaya gaya hai, aur uska pani mahndi ke arq jaisa hai aur iskey khajoor ke darkht shayatin ke saron jaisey hain.'' isliye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey niklwa diya. muttafaq aleh."
5894,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maale-ghanimat taqseem farma rahey they, itney mein bano Tameem qabiley se Zul-Khuwesra naami shakhs aaya aur usney kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! insaf karen, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par afsos ! agar main adl nahin karunga to phir aur kon adl karega, agar main adl na karun to main bhi khaaib (bad-nasib) aur khaasir (nuqsan uthaneywala) ho jaaun.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, mujhey ijazat farmaain ke main uski gardan maar dun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do ke uskey kuchh sathi hongey tum mein se koi apni Namaz ko unki Namaz ke muqabley mein , apney rozey unke rozon ke muqabley mein maamuli samjheyga , wo Quran padhengey lekin wo unke halaq se nichey nahin utreyga, wo Deen se is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer shikar se paar ho jata hai, us (teer) ke paikaan, uskey putthey par jo ke paikaan par lapetaa jata hai aur teer ke us hissey ko jo ke par aur paikaan ke darmiyan hota hai ko dekha jaey to is par koi nishan nazar nahin aaeyga , halanke wo (teer) gobar aur khoon mein se guzarta hai, unki nishani ye hai ke eik siyah faam shakhs hai uska eik bazu aurat ke pistaan ki tarah (utha hua) hoga ya hiltey huey gosht ke tukdey ki tarah hoga, aur wo logon ke behtareen giroh ke khilaf baghawat karengey.'' Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main gawahi deta hun ke maine ye hadees Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se ladaai ladi hai aur main Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha, us shakhs ke mutalliq hukm diya gaya to usey talash kiya gaya aur usey laya gaya yahan tak ke maine usey dekha to uska pura huliya bilkul isi tarah tha jis tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska huliya bayan kiya tha. eik dusri riwayat mein hai, eik aadmi aaya, uski aankhen dhansi hui thin, peshani ubhri hui thi, dadhi ghani thi, gaalein phooli hui thin, sar mundaa hua tha, usney kaha, Muhammad ! Allah se dar jaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main Allah ki nafarmani karunga to phir aur kon us se darega, Allah ne zamin walon par mujhey ameen bana kar bheja hai jabkey tum mujhey ameen nahin samajhtey ho.'' eik aadmi ne usey qatl karney ki darkhast ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey rok diya, jab wo wapis gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us shakhs ke nasab se kuchh aisey log paida hongey jo Quran padhengey lekin wo unke halaq se nichey nahin utrega, wo Islam se is tarah khaarij ho jaeyngey jis tarah teer shikar se paar ho jata hai, wo ehale-Islam ko qatl karengey aur but paraston ko chhod dengey, agar maine unhen pa liya to main unhen qome-Aad ki tarah qatl karunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5895,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apni mushrik walida ko Islam ki dawat pesh karta tha, eik roz maine usey dawat pesh ki to usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki shaan mein kuchh aisey alfaz kahey jo mujhey nagawar guzrey, main rotaa hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah se dua farmaain ke wo Abu-Hurera ki walida ko hidayat nasib farma dey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Abu-Hurera ki walida ko hidayat ata farma.'' main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki dua par khush hota hua wahan se chala , jab main darwazey par pahuncha to wo band tha, meri walida ne merey qadmon ki aahat sun kar farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! apni jagah par thehar jaao, maine pani girney ki aawaz sun li thi, unhoney ghusl kiya, apni qamis pehni, aur ujlat mein chadar bhi na li aur darwaza khol kar farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! main gawahi deti hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur main gawahi deti hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain, main khushi ke aansu bahaataa hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas wapis aaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ka shukr ada kiya aur duaaey khair farmaee. rawahu Muslim."
5896,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, tum log kehtey ho ke Abu-Hurera , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bahut ziyada hadise bayan karta hai. Allah ki qism ! eik din Allah ke paas jana hai, merey Muhajir bhai bazaron mein kharid aur farokht mein mashghool raha kartey they aur merey ansaar bhai apney amwaal (kheton aur baaghaat) mein mashghool raha kartey they, main eik miskeen aadmi tha, main apna pet bhadney ke baad phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rehta , eik roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs meri is guftgu ke pura honey tak kapda bichhaaey rakhega, phir usey apney seeney ke sath laga lega to wo merey faraameen mein se kuch bhi nahin bhoolega.'' maine dhaari daar chadar bichha di uskey ilawa merey paas koi aur kapda nahin rehta tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab apni guftgu mukammal farmaai, to maine chadar ko apney seeney ke sath laga liya, us zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja ! main us roz se aaj tak aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke faraameen se kuchh nahin bhoolaa. muttafaq aleh."
5897,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya tum mujhey Zul-Khalasa (but) se aaram nahin pahunchatey?'' maine arz kiya, kyon nahin, zarur , lekin main ghodey ki sawari achchhi tarah nahin kar paata tha, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya to aapney apna haath merey seeney par maara yahan tak ke maine aap ke haath ke asraat apney seeney mein mehsus kiye , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! isko (ghodey ki pusht par) sabaat (mazbuti) ata farma, usey hidayat ki raah dikhaney wala aur hidayat yafta bana.'' wo bayan kartey hain, uskey baad main apney ghodey se nahin gira, wo Ahmas qabiley ke dedh sau (150) ghud sawaron ke sath rawana huey aur usey aag ke sath jala diya aur usey tod diya. muttafaq aleh."
5898,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye (wahi) likha karta tha, wo Islam se murtad ho kar mushrekin se ja mila to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zamin usey qubul nahin karegi.'' Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke wo shakhs jis jagah faut hua tha wo wahan gaey to unhoney usey satah zamin par pada hua dekha to puchha : uska kya maamla hai? unhoney bataya ke ham ne usey kaee martaba dafn kiya magar zamin (qabr) isey qubul nahin karti. muttafaq aleh."
5899,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye us waqt Suraj ghurub ho chuka tha, aapney eik aawaz suni to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahudiyon ko unki qabron mein azab diya ja raha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5900,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik safar se wapis tashrif laye, jab aap Madina ke qarib pahunchey to aisi tez hawa chali , qarib tha ke wo sawar ko chupa deti, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye hawa kisi munafiq ki maut ke waqt chalai gaee hai.'' aap Madina pahunchey to munafiqon ka eik bada aadmi faut ho chuka tha. rawahu Muslim."
5901,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey yahan tak ke ham Asfan pahunchey to aapney chand roz wahan qiyam farmaya , to baaz  munafiq) logon ne kaha : yahan to ham bila maqsad thehrey hain, hamarey ehale w ayaal peechhey hain, hamein unka khatra hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak ye baat pahunchi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! Madina ki her ghaati aur her darrey par do farishtey pehra dey rahey hain yahan tak ke tum wahan wapis chaley jaao.'' phir farmaya : ''kooch karo.'' ham ne kooch kiya aur Madina ki taraf wapis paltey, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! jab ham Madina mein dakhil huey to ham ne abhi apna saman nahin utara tha ke bano Abdullah bin Ghatfaan ne ham par hamla kar diya, is se pehley koi chiz unhen aamada nahin karti thi. rawahu Muslim."
5902,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein log qehat saali (sukhe) ka shikar ho gaey, us doran ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba Juma irshad farma rahey they, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) khada hua aur usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maal maweshi halak ho gaey, baal bachchey bhook ka shikar ho gaey, Allah se hamarey liye dua farmaeyn, aapney haath buland farmaai , us waqt ham aasman par badal ka tukda tak nahin dekh rahey they, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! aapney abhi unhen nichey nahin kiya tha ke pahadon ki tarah badal chha gaey, phir aap apney member se nichey nahin utrey they ke maine barish ke qatrey aap ki dadhi Mubarak par girtey huey dekhey, us roz agley roz yahan tak ke doosrey Jumey tak barish hoti rahi phir doosrey Jume ko wohi Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ya koi aur shakhs khada hua aur usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! makaan gir gaey, maal doob gaya, aap Allah se hamarey liye dua farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haath uthaey aur dua farmaee : ''aey Allah ! hamarey Aas paas barish barsa , ham par na barsa.'' aap badalon ke jis koney ki taraf ishara farmatey to udhar se badal chhat jata aur Madina hoz ki tarah bin chuka tha, jabkey wadi qanaa ka naala mahina bhar behta raha, aur Madine ke Aas paas se jo bhi aata wo khub sairaabi ki baat karta. eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah hamarey Aas paas barish barsa, ham par na barse, aey Allah ! teelon par, pahadon par, wadiyon mein aur darakhton ke ugney ki jagahon par barish barsa.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, barish tham gaee aur ham nikley to ham dhoop mein chal rahey they. muttafaq aleh."
5903,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farmatey to aap masjid ke sutonon mein se khajoor ke taney ke sath tek lagaya kartey they, jab aap ke liye member bana diya gaya to aap is par khadey ho gaey, chunanche aap jis khajoor ke taney ke paas khutba irshad farmaya kartey they wo cheekhney chillaney laga : yahan tak ke qarib tha ke wo phat jata, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (member sey) nichey utrey, usey pakda aur usey apney sath milaya to wo us bachchey ki tarah roney laga jisey khamosh karaya jata hai, yahan tak ke wo khamosh ho gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jo zikr suna karta tha ab wo us se mehroom ho gaya hai isliye wo roya tha.'' Bukhari."
5904,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas baaein hath se khaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney daain haath se khaao.'' usney kaha : main taqat nahin rakhta, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to istataat na rakhey.'' us shakhs ko takabbur hi ne roka tha, raawi bayan kartey hain, wo phir us (daeyn haath) ko apney munh tak nahin utha sakta tha. rawahu Muslim."
5905,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik martaba Madina waley ghabrahat ka shikar ho gaey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abu-Talha ke ghodey par , jis par zeen nahin thi, Sawar ho gaey, wo sust raftaar tha, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis tashrif laye to farmaya : ''ham ne tumharey is ghodey ko darya (yani tez raftaar) paya.'' phir uskey baad ye ghoda kisi doosrey ghodey ko qarib phatakney nahin deta tha, eik dusri riwayat mein hai is roz ke baad koi ghoda uskey aagey nahin badh saka. Bukhari."
5906,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jis waqt merey walid faut huey to wo maqrooz they, maine unke qarz khuwahon ko pesh kaash! ki ke wo uskey qarz ke barabar khajuren ley lein , lekin unhoney inkar kar diya, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya, aap jantey hi hain ke merey walid ghazwae uhad mein Shahid kar diye gaey they, aur unhoney bahut sa qarz chhoda hai, aur main chahta hun ke wo qarz chahey (chaahe) aap ko (merey yahan) dekh lein , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''jaao her qism ki khajoor alag alag jama karo.'' maine aisey hi kiya, phir aap ko dawat di, jab qarz khuwahon (chahne walon) ne aap ki taraf dekha to mujh par sakht naraz huye, jab aapney unka tarze-amal dekha to aapney sab se badey dher ke gird teen chakkar lagaey phir is par beth gaey, phir farmaya : ''apney qarz khuwahon (chahne walon) ko bulaao.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen naap kar ada farmatey rahey yahan tak ke Allah ne merey walid ka sara qarz ada kar diya aur main khush tha ke Allah ne merey walid ka qarz ada farma diya, aur (mera khayal tha ke) main apni behnon ke liye eik khajoor bhi lekar na ja sakoonga , lekin Allah ne sarey dher bacha diye yahan tak ke main us dher ki taraf , jis par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bethey huey they, dekh raha hun ke wo isi tarah hai ke jis tarah us se eik khajoor bhi kam nahin hui. Bukhari."
5907,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) apney eik mishkeezey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ghi ka hadiya pesh kiya karti thin, unke bete unke paas aatey aur salan maangtey aur unke paas kuchh na hota to wo us mishkeezey ka qasd (irada) (iraada) kartin jis mein wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hadiya bheja karti thin, wo is mein ghi paatin, aur unke ghar mein hamesha hi salan raha yahan tak ke usney us (mishkeezey) ko nichod liya, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aayin to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne usey nichod liya hai? '' Umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum usey chhod detin to wo wesey hi rehta.'' rawahu Muslim."
5908,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aawaz kamzor si suni hai, jis se maine bhook ka andaza lagaya hai, kya tumharey paas koi chiz hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan, unhoney jau ki chand rotiyaan nikalin, phir apni odhni nikali aur rotiyon ko lapet kar chadar ke eik koney mein baandh kar merey haath mein thamaa diya, phir mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya, main wo lekar chala gaya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid mein paya aur aap ke sath kuchh log bhi they, maine unhen salam kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''tujhey Abu-Talha ne bheja hai? ''maine arz kiya : ji haan ! aapney farmaya : ''khana de-kar?'' maine arz kya : ji haan ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haazirin se farmaya : ''khadey ho jaao.'' aap chaley aur main unke aagey aagey chal raha tha yahan tak ke maine Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunch kar unhen bataya to Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Umme-Sulaim ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chand sathiyon ke sath tashrif laye hain, jabkey hamarey paas to aisi koi chiz nahin jo unhen khilaney ke liye pesh kar saken, unhoney farmaya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) gaey yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mulaqat ki, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tashrif laye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Sulaim ! tumharey paas jo kuchh hai wo ley aao.'' wo wohi rotiyaan ley aayin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman par un rotiyon ka choora kiya gaya aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne un par ghi ka mishkeeza nichodaa aur usey salan banaya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us khaney ke barey mein wo dua farmaee jo Allah Taala ne chahi phir farmaya : ''das aadmiyon ko bulaao, unhen bulaya gaya unhoney sair ho (pait bhar) kar khana khaya , phir wo chaley gaey, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''das ko bulaao, is tarah sab logon ne sair ho kar khana khaya, wo sattar ya assi afrad they. aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''das afrad ko bulaao.'' wo aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka naam lekar khaao.'' unhoney khaya yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne assi afrad se aisey hi farmaya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur ghar walon ne khaya aur khana bach bhi gaya. aur Sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas das aadmi bhejo, yahan tak ke aapney chaalis afrad giney, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khana khaya, main dekhney laga ke kya is mein koi kami aati hai? aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayaat mein, phir jo khana bach gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ikhatta kiya, phir uskey liye barkat ki dua farmaee to wo jitna tha utna hi ho gaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey ley lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
5909,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zauraa ke maqam par they ke eik bartan aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya, aapney apna daste-mubarak bartan mein rakha to aap ki ungliyon se pani phootney laga , Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se wuzu kiya, Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : tum kitney they? unhoney farmaya , teen sau ya taqriban teen sau. muttafaq aleh."
5910,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham to aayaat aur mojzat ko baaise-barkat shumar kiya kartey they jabkey tum unhen baaise-khauf samajhtey ho, ham eik martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareeke-safar they ke pani kam pad gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo pani bach gaya hai usey lekar aao.'' wo eik bartan laye jis mein thoda sa pani tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna daste-mubarak bartan mein dakhil farmaya , phir farmaya : ''mubarak pani hasil karo aur barkat Allah ki taraf se hui hai.'' aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ungliyon se pani phoot'tey huey dekha, aur khana khaney ke doran ham khaney ki tasbih suna kartey they. Bukhari."
5911,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba irshad farmaya to is mein farmaya : ''tum raat bhar safar karney ke baad Insha-Allah kal pani tak pahunch jaaogey.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) chaltey gaey koi kisi taraf iltifaat (tawajjoh) nahin kar raha tha, Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar kar rahey they yahan tak ke aadhi raat ho gaee to aap raastey se hat kar eik jagah sar Mubarak rakh kar soney lagey aur farmaya : ''hamari Namaz ka khayal rakhna.'' sab se pehley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi bedaar huey us waqt Suraj tulu ho chuka tha, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sawaariyon par Sawar ho jaao.'' ham Sawar ho gaey aur safar shuru kar diya yahan tak ke jab Suraj buland ho gaya to aapney padaaw dala, phir aapney pani ka bartan mangaayaa jo ke merey paas tha, is mein kuchh pani tha, aapney ehtiyat ke sath us se wuzu farmaya, raawi bayan kartey hain, is mein thoda sa pani bach gaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamarey liye is pani ki hifazat karo, an-qareeb us bartan ko badi azmat hasil hogi.'' phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz ke liye Azan di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do rakatein padhin, phir namaze-Fajr ada ki, aap sawar huey to ham bhi aap ke sath hi Sawar ho gaey, aur ham logon ke paas pahunchey to din achchhi tarah chadh chuka tha aur her chiz garm ho chuki thi, log keh rahey they : Allah ke Rasool ! ham (loo ki wajeh sey) halak ho gaey aur piyasey ho gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum halak nahin hogey.'' aapney pani ka bartan mangaayaa , aap undel rahey they aur Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) unhen pila rahey they, logon ne pani ka bartan dekha to wo is par jhuk gaey (umad aaye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney akhlaq sanwaaro, tum sab sairab ho jaaogey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney taameel ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) undel rahey they aur main unhen pila raha tha, yahan tak ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi baqi reh gaey, phir aapney pani undela aur mujhey farmaya : ''piyo.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main aap se pehley nahin piyunga, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ko pilaney wala sab se aakhir par peeta hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine piya aur phir aapney piya, raawi bayan kartey hain, log sairab ho kar rahat ke sath pani par aaye. rawahu Muslim. isi tarah sahih Muslim mein hai aur kitabul-humaidi aur Jaame al-usool mein isi tarah hai, aur masaabeh mein lafz ( آخرھم (ke baad lafz ( شربا (ka izafa hai."
5912,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-tabuk ke moqe par Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) sakht bhook ka shikar ho gaey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! un se zayed zaade-raah talab farmaain phir Allah se unke liye is mein barkat ki dua farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , theek hai.'' aapney chamdey ka dasterkhaan mangaayaa , usey bichha diya gaya, phir aapney un se bacha hua zaade-raah talab farmaya, koi aadmi mutthi bhar makai laya , koi mutthi bhar khajoor laya , aur koi roti ka tukda laya, yahan tak ke dasterkhaan par thodi si chiz jama ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne barkat ke liye dua farmaee phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney bartan bhar lo.'' unhoney apney bartan bhar liye yahan tak ke unhoney lashkar ke tamam bartan bhar liye , raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney khub sair ho kar khaya yahan tak ke khana bach bhi gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur ye ke main Allah ka Rasool hun, jo shakhs yaqin ke sath shahaadaton ka iqrar karta hai to wo jannat se nahin roka jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5913,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) se shaadi hui to meri walida Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne khajoor , ghi aur paneer lekar hees banaya aur usey handiya jaisey bartan mein rakha , aur farmaya : Anas ! isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley jaao, aur unhen kaho : isey meri walida ne aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya hai aur wo aap ko salam arz karti hain, aur unhoney ye bhi arz kiya hai ke Allah ke Rasool ! ye hamari taraf se aap ki khidmat mein qaleel (yani haqeer) sa hadiya hai, main gaya, aur arz kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey rakh do.'' phir farmaya : ''jaao ! falan falan aur falan shakhs ko bula laao.'' aur aapney unke naam bhi bataey'' aur jo bhi tujhey miley usey bula laao.'' aapney jinkey naam bataey they, mein unhen aur jo log raastey mein mujhey miley to main unhen bula laya, main wapis aaya to ghar bhar chuka tha, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : tum kitney log they? unhoney farmaya : taqriban teen sau, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney us Heesa (halwey) mein apna daste-mubarak rakha aur jo Allah ne chaha wo dua farmaee, phir aap das das aadmiyon ko bulatey rahey aur wo us se khatey rahey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen farmatey : ''Allah ka naam lo, aur her shakhs apney samney se khaye.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, un sab ne khub sair ho kar kha liya, eik giroh nikalta to doosra giroh dakhil ho jata, yahan tak ke un sab ne kha liya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' Anas ! (isey) utha lo.'' maine utha liya, main nahin janta ke jab maine (hees) rakha tha tab ziyada tha ya jab maine uthaya tha tab ziyada tha. muttafaq aleh."
5914,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik ghazwe mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareek tha, main pani laney waley eik oont par Sawar tha, wo thak chuka tha aur wo chalney ke qabil nahin raha tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to farmaya : ''terey oont ko kya hua hai? ''maine arz kiya, wo thak chuka hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peechey gaey aur usey daantaa aur uskey liye dua farmaee, phir wo doosrey oonton ke aagey aagey chalta raha , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''tumharey oont ka kya haal hai? ''maine arz kiya : behtar hai, aap ki barkat ka is par asar ho gaya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum isey chaalis dirham ke ba-ewaz bechogey?'' maine us shart par usey bech diya ke Madina tak main usi par safar karunga, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina pahunchey to agley roz main oont lekar hazire-khidmat hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey uski qeemat ata farma di wo oont bhi mujhey wapis dey diya. muttafaq aleh."
5915,"Hazrat Abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huye, ham wadi Quraa main eik aurat ke baagh ke paas pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us (ke phalon) ka andaza lagaao.'' ham ne andaza lagaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska das wasq ka andaza lagaya, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isko yad rakhna yahan tak ke agar Allah ne chaha to ham tumharey paas wapis aaeyngey.'' aur ham chaltey gaey yahan tak ke ham tabuk pahunch gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj raat badey zor ki aandhi chaley gi, is mein koi shakhs khada na ho aur jis shakhs ke paas oont ho to wo usey baandh ley.'' zor ki aandhi chal , eik aadmi khada hua to aandhi ne usey utha kar jabal-tai par ja phenka. phir ham wapis aaye yahan tak ke ham wadi Quraa pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aurat se uskey baagh ke phal ke mutalliq puchha ke'' uskey phal kitney huey they?'' usney arz kiya : das wasq. muttafaq aleh."
5916,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum an-qareeb Misr Fateh karogey, aur wo aisi sarzameen hai jiski currency qiraat hai. jab tum usey Fateh kar lo to wahan ke bashindon se husne-suluk karna. kyonkey unhen hurmat aur qurbat ka haq hasil hai.'' ya farmaya : ''unhen hurmat aur rishtae-sasuraal ka haq hasil hai. aur jab tum do aadmiyon ko eent barabar jagah par jhagda kartey huey dekho to wahan se kooch kar jana.'' aur maine Abdur-Rehman bin Shurehbil bin Hasna aur uskey bhai Rabeea ko eik eent barabar par jhagda kartey huey dekha to main wahan se nikal aaya. rawahu Muslim."
5917,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey Sahaba mein.'' eik riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein baara munafiq hongey wo jannat mein dakhil hongey na uski khushbu paeyngey, yahan tak ke oont sooi ke nakay mein se guzar jaey. un mein se aath ko to wo phodaa hi kafi hai, (uskey ilawa) aag ka eik shola jo unke kandhon ke darmiyan zahir hoga yahan tak ke uski haraarat ka asar unke seenon (yani dilon) par mehsus hoga.'' rawahu Muslim . aur ham Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : (لأ عطین ھذا الرأیۃ غدا) baab manaaqib Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (من یصعد الشنیۃ)  (باب جامع المناقب)  mein Insha-Allah taala zikr karengey."
5918,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Abu Talib, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Quraish ke srdaaron ke sath mein Sham ke liye rawana huye, jab wo raahib ke paas pahunchey to unhoney uskey yahaan padaaw dal kar apni sawaariyon ke kajawey khol diye, itney mein raahib unke paas aaya, wo is se pehley bhi yahan se guzra kartey they, lekin wo unke paas nahin aata tha, raawi bayan kartey hain, wo apni sawaariyon ke kajawey utaar rahey they to raahib unke darmiyan kisi ko talash karta phir raha tha yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunch gaya, usney aap ka daste Mubarak pakad kar kaha : ye Saiyedul Aalemeen hain, ye Rabul Aalemeen ke Rasool hain, Allah inhen Rahmatul Aalemeen banakar mab-us farmaeyga (bhejega). is par Quraish ke sardaron ne puchha : tumharey ilm ki buniyad kya hai? usney kaha : jab tum ghaati par chadhey to her shajr aur Hajar (paid aur patthar) aap ke samney jhuk gaya, aur wo sirf kisi Nabi ki khatir hi jhuktey hain, aur main mohare-nabuwat se bhi unhen pehchanta hun jo unke shaaney ki haddi ke nichey saib ki manind hai, phir wo wapis gaya aur unke liye khaney ka ehtimam kiya, jab wo khana lekar unke paas aaya to us waqt aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) oonton ki charaagaah mein they, usney kaha : unhen bula bhejo, jab aap tashrif laye to badal ka tukda aap par saya kiye tha, jab aap akeley qom ke paas aaye to wo log aap se pehley hi darkht ke saye mein ja chukey they. jab aap beth gaey to darkht ka saya jhuk gaya, usney kaha : darkht ke saye ko dekho ke wo un par jhuk gaya hai, usney kaha : main tumhen Allah ki qism de-kar poochhta hun ke tum mein se inka sarparast kon hai? unhoney bataya , Abu Talib, wo musalsal unko qism deta raha (ke aap unhen wapis ley jaeyn) yahan tak ke Abu Talib ne unhen wapis bhej diya, aur Abu-Bakar ne Bilal ko aap ke sath rawana kiya, aur raahib ne roti aur zaitun bator zaade-rah aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ata kiya. rawahu Tirmizi."
5919,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Makka mein mojud tha, ham uski eik janib nikley to samney aaney wala her shajr aur hajar (paid aur patthar) keh raha tha : Allah ke Rasool ! Assalamualaikum ! rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
5920,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Mairaj ki raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas burraaq laee gaee jisey lagaam dali gaee thi aur is par zeen sajaai gaee thi, usney aap ke bethney mein rukawat paida ki to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne usey farmaya : kya tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ye sulook karti ho? Allah ke yahan un se badh kar moazziz kisi shakhsiyat ne tujh par sawari nahin ki hogi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(ye sun kar) wo (burraaq) paseeney se shrabor ho gaee. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5921,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ham baitul-Maqdis pahunchey to Jibrael ne apni ungli se ishara farmaya to uskey sath pathar mein surakh kar diya aur uskey sath burraaq ko baandh diya.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5922,"Hazrat Ya'alaa bin Murra Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se teen mojzat dekhey, ham safar kar rahey they ke ham eik oont ke paas se guzrey is par pani laya jata tha, jab us oont ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to wo bulbula utha aur apni gardan (zameen par) rakh di, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan thehar gaey aur farmaya : ''is oont ka maalik kahan hai? '' wo aap ki khidmat mein aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey mujhey farokht kar do.'' usney arz kiya, nahin, ham Allah ke Rasool ! aap ko wesey hi hiba kar detey hain, lekin arz ye hai ke ye jis gharaney ka hai unki maeeshat ka inhisaar (rozi roti ka daaromadaar) sirf isi par hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun ley jab to ne uski ye surat bayan ki to isney kaam ki ziyadti aur khurak ki qillat shikaayat ki thi tum iskey sath achchha suluk karo.'' phir ham ne safar shuru kiya yahan tak ke ham ne eik jagah qiyam kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so gaey, eik darkht zamin phadta hua aaya yahan tak ke usney aap ko dhanp liya, aur phir wapis apni jagah par chala gaya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bedaar huey to maine aap se uska zikr kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye wo darkht hai jisney apney rab se ijazat talab ki ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam karey lihaza usey ijazat di gaee.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : phir ham ne safar shuru kiya to ham pani ke qarib se guzrey wahan eik aurat apney majnun bete ko lekar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey uski naak se pakad kar farmaya : ''nikal ja, kyonkey main Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ka Rasool hun.'' phir ham ne safar shuru kar diya, jab ham wapis aaye aur usi pani ke maqam se guzrey to aapney us aurat se us bachchey ke mutalliq daryaft farmaya to usney arz kiya, us zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja ! ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad uski taraf se koi nagawar chiz nahin dekhi. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5923,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aurat apna beta lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey bete ko jinon hai, aur isey subah aur Sham iska daurah padta hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey seeney par haath phera aur dua farmaee to usney eik zor daar qai ki to uskey pet se kaley kuttey ka pilla daudta hua nikal gaya. rawahu Darmi."
5924,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas tashrif laye jabkey aap ghamgin bethey huey they aur aap Makka walon ke naajaaiz sulook se khoon se rangin ho chukey they, unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap pasand kartey hain ke ham aap ko eik nishani dikhayen? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne aap ke peechhey se eik darkht dekha, aur farmaya : usey bulaeyn , aapney usey bulaya to wo aaya aur aap ke samney khada ho gaya, phir aapney kaha : isey wapis janey ka hukm farmaeyn, unhoney usey hukm farmaya to wo wapis chala gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey liye kafi hai, merey liye kafi hai.'' rawahu Darmi."
5925,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) aaya, jab wo qarib aa gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' usney kaha, aap jo farma rahey hain is par kon gawahi deta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kaante-daar darkht.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur wo wadi ke kinarey par tha, wo zamin phadta hua aaya yahan tak ke wo aap ke samney khada ho gaya. aapney us se teen martaba gawahi talab ki to usney teen martaba gawahi di ke aap ki shaan wohi hai jaisey ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai, phir wo apni ugney ki jagah par chala gaya. rawahu Darmi."
5926,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein haazir hua aur usney arz kiya, mujhey kis tarah pata chaley ke aap Nabi hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main khajoor ke us darkht se us khoshay ko bulaaun aur wo gawahi dey ke main Allah ka Rasool hun (to phir theek hai).'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya to wo khajoor ke darkht se utar kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh ho gaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wapis chaley jaao.'' wo wapis chala gaya, aur Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ne Islam qubul kar liya. Tirmizi, aur unhoney isey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5927,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik bhediya bakriyon ke rewad ke charwahey ke paas aaya aur usney wahan se eik bakri uthali, charwahey ne uska peechha kiya yahan tak ke usko us se chuda liya, raawi bayan kartey hain, bhediya eik tiley par chadh gaya, aur wahan peeth ke bal beth gaya aur dam dono paaon ke darmiyan dakhil kar li , phir usney kaha : maine rozi ka qasd (irada) (irada) kiya jo Allah ne mujhey ata ki thi aur maine usey hasil kar liya tha, magar tu ney isey mujh se chuda liya. us aadmi ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine aaj ke din ki tarah koi bhediya boltey huey nahin dekha, bhediye ne kaha is se bhi ajeeb baat ye hai ke aadmi (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) jo do pahadon ke darmiyan waqey nakhlistan (Madina) mein rehta hai, wo tumhen maazi aur haal ke waqiyat ke mutalliq batata hai. raawi bayan kartey hain, wo shakhs Yahudi tha, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to usney us waqie ke mutalliq aap ko bataya aur Islam qubul kar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski tasdeeq farmaee, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye qiyamat se pehley ki nishaniyan hain, qarib hai ke aadmi (ghar sey) nikley, phir wo wapis aaye to uskey jootey aur uska kodaa usey un halaat ke mutalliq bataeyn jo uskey baad uskey ehle khana ke sath pesh aaye hon.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5928,"Hazrat Abul-Ala, Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik bartan se din bhar baari baari tanaawul kartey (khaana khate) rahey, wo is tarah ke das kha jatey aur das aa jatey. ham ne kaha : kahan se badhaya ja raha tha? unhon (Samura (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : tum kis chiz se tajjub kartey ho? is mein izafa to us taraf se ho raha tha, aur unhoney apney haath se aasman ki taraf ishara farmaya. rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
5929,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Badr ke roz teen sau pandarah Sahaba kiram ke sath rawana huye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! ye nangey paaon hain to inhen sawari ata farma , aey Allah ! ye nangey badan hain to inhen libas ata farma, aey Allah ! ye bhook ka shikar hain to inhen pait bhar khaana khila.'' Allah ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Fateh ata farmaee, aap wapis aaye to un mein se her aadmi ke paas eik ya do oont they, unke paas libas bhi tha aur unke pait bhare hue they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5930,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari (dushman ke khilaf) madad ki jaeygi, tum maale-ghanimat hasil karogey, tum (bahut se mulk) Fateh karogey, tum mein se jo shakhs ye mazkura chizen pa ley to wo Allah se darey, neki ka hukm karey aur burai se mana karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5931,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ehle khaibar ki eik Yahudi aurat ne eik bhuni hui bakri mein zahar mila diya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hadiya ke taur par bhej diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dasti li aur us se khaya , aur aap ke chand Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi aap ke sath khaya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney haath (khaney sey) utha lo.'' aapney Yahudi aurat ko bula bheja aur farmaya : ''kya to ne is bakri mein zahar milaya tha?'' usney kaha : aap ko kis ne bataya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey haath mein ye jo dasti hai usney mujhey bataya hai.'' usney arz kiya : ji haan , maine kaha : agar to wo sachchey Nabi huey to ye usey nuqsan nahin pahunchaegi, aur agar wo sachchey Nabi na huey to ham us se aaram pa jaeyngey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko maaf farma diya aur usey saza na di, aur aap ke jin Sahaba kiram ne bakri ka gosht khaya tha wo faut ho gaey, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bakri ka gosht khaney ki wajeh se apney kandhon ke darmiyan pachhney lagwaaey, Abu Hind jo ke ansaar qabiley bano biyaaza ke azad karda ghulam they, unhoney seeng aur chhuri ke sath aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke pachhney lagaey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
5932,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwae-Hunain ke moqe par unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar kiya, unhoney safar jari rakha yahan tak ke pichhlaa pahar ho gaya, eik ghud sawar aaya aur usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main falan falan pahad ke ooper chadha hun aur maine achcha Hawazin qabiley ko dekha hai ke wo sab ke sab apney maweshiyon aur apney amwaal ke sath Hunain ki taraf ikhattey ho rahey hain, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : ''Insha-Allah taala kal wo musalmanon ka maale-ghanimat hoga.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj raat hamara pehra kon dega?'' Anas bin Abi-Mursad Al Ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sawar ho jaao.'' wo apney ghodey par Sawar huye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us ghaati ki taraf jaao yahan tak ke tum uski choti par pahunch jaao.'' jab subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni jaey Namaz par tashrif ley gaey aur do rakaat Namaz ada ki, phir farmaya : ''kya tum ne apney ghud sawar ko mehsus kiya?'' eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham ne mehsus nahin kiya, Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dorane-namaz us ghaati ki taraf iltifaat (tawajjoh) farmatey rahey yahan tak ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to farmaya : ''khush ho jaao , tumhara ghud sawar aa gaya hai.'' ham bhi darakhton ke darmiyan us ghaati ki taraf dekhney lagey to wo achcha aa gaya yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa kar khada ho gaya to usney arz kiya, main chalta gaya yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq us ghaati ke buland tareen hissey par tha, jab subah hui to main un dono ghaatiyon ke atraaf se ho aaya hun, lekin maine kisi ko nahin dekha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''kya raat ke waqt tum (apney ghodey sey) nichey utrey they?'' unhoney arz kiya : Namaz padhney ya qazaey-hajat ke ilawa main nahin utra, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum is (raat) ke baad koi bhi nek amal na karo to tum par koi muwaakhiza (pakad) nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5933,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main kuchh khajuren lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! in mein barkat ke liye dua farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ikhatta kiya phir merey liye un mein barkat ki dua farmaai , aur farmaya : ''inhen ley lo aur unhen apney tosha daan mein rakh lo, jab bhi tum in mein se kuchh lena chaho to is mein apna haath dal kar ley lena aur unhen mukammal taur par bahar na nikalna.'' maine un mein se itney itney wasq khajoor Allah ki raah mein ata kiye , ham khud bhi is mein se khatey they aur khilatey bhi they, aur wo meri kamar se alag nahin hota tha yahan tak ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke roz wo munqata' ho (toot) kar gir pada. rawahu Tirmizi."
5934,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Quraish ne eik raat Makka mein (Daarun nadwa mein) mashwara kiya to un mein se kisi ne kaha jab subah ho to usko qaid kar do, unki murad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) they, kisi ne kaha : nahin, balke usey qatl kar do, aur kisi ne kaha, nahin balke usey (Makka sey) nikal bahar karo, Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is (mansoobey) ki ittila kar di, us raat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bistar par raat basar ki aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se chal diye yahan tak ke aap ghaar mein pahunch gaey, jabkey mushrekin puri raat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) par pehra detey rahey aur wo samajhtey rahey ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. jab subah hui to wo un par hamla aawar huey jab unhoney dekha ke ye to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain, Allah ne unka mansuba nakam bana diya, unhoney puchha : tumhara sathi kahan hai? unhoney farmaya : main nahin janta. unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qadmon ke nishaanaat ka pata lagaya, jab wo pahad par pahunchey to un par maamla shubeh mein pad gaya, wo pahad par chadh gaey aur ghaar ke paas se guzrey , unhoney uskey darwazey par makdi ka jaalaa dekha, aur unhoney kaha : agar wo is mein dakhil huey hotey to uskey darwazey par makdi ka jaalaa na hota, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wahan teen roz qiyam farmaya. rawahu Ahmed."
5935,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab khaibar Fateh hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik bakri ka hadiya pesh kiya gaya jis mein zahar tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahan jitney Yahudi mojud hain unhen merey paas jama karo.'' chunanche wo sab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kar diye gaey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''main tum se eik chiz ke mutalliq sawal karney laga hun kya tum uskey mutalliq mujhey sach sach bataaogey?'' unhoney kaha : ji haan ! Abul-Qaasim ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : '' tumhara baap kon they?'' unhoney bataya : falan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jhoot boltey ho, balke tumhara baap to falan hai.'' unhoney kaha : aapney sach farmaya aur achchhaa kiya phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main tum se kisi chiz ke mutalliq daryaft karun to tum mujhey sach sach bataaogey?'' unhoney kaha : ji haan, Abul-Qaasim ! agar ham ne aap se jhoot bola to aap samajh jaeyngey jis tarah aapney hamarey baap ke barey mein (hamara jhoot) jaan liya tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''jahannami kon hain?'' unhoney kaha : kuchh muddat ke liye ham is mein jaeyngey, phir hamari jagah tum wahan aa jaaogey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum hi is mein zaleel ho kar rahogey , kyonkey ham is mein tumhari jagah kabhi bhi dakhil nahin hongey.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tum se eik chiz ke barey mein sawal karta hun kya tum mujhey sach sach jawab dogey?'' unhoney kaha : haan , Abul-Qaasim ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya tum ne is bakri (ke gosht) mein zahar milaya hai? '' unhoney kaha : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kis chiz ne tumhen is par aamada kiya?'' unhoney kaha : ham ne isliye kiya ke agar aap jhootey huey to hamein aap se aaram mil jaeyga aur agar aap sachchey huey to aap ko nuqsan nahin pahunchega. Bukhari."
5936,"Hazrat umr bin Akhtab Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Fajr ki Namaz padhaai aur member par tashrif ley gaey, hamein khitab farmaya yahan tak ke Zohar ka waqt ho gaya phir aap member se utrey aur Namaz padhaai phir member par tashrif ley gaey aur hamein khitab farmaya yahan tak ke namaze-Asr ka waqt ho gaya, phir aap nichey tashrif laye aur Namaz padhaai, phir member par tashrif ley gaey aur (khitab farmaya) yahan tak ke Suraj ghurub ho gaya aapney qiyamat tak honey waley waqiyat ke mutalliq hamein bayan farmaya , raawi bayan kartey hain, ham mein se ziyada aalim wo hai jo is khutbey ko ham mein se ziyada yad rakhney wala hai. rawahu Muslim."
5937,"Hazrat Ma'an bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain maine apney walid se suna, unhoney kaha : maine Masruq se puchha jis raat jinnon ne Quran suna tha uski khabar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kis ne di thi? unhoney bataya : mujhey tumharey walid yani Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke unke mutalliq eik darkht ne ittilaa di thi. muttafaq aleh."
5938,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka aur Madina ke darmiyan they, ham ne chaand dekhney ka ehtimam kiya, meri nazar tez thi, lihaza maine usey dekh liya , aur merey siwa kisi ne na kaha ke usney usey dekha hai, main umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney laga : kya aap usey dekh nahin rahey? wo usey nahin dekh pa rahey they, raawi bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey , main an-qareeb usey dekh lunga. main apney bistar par letaa hua tha, phir unhoney ehle Badr ke mutalliq hamein batana shuru kiya, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Badr ke moqe par kuffar ke qatl gaahon ke mutalliq eik roz pehley hi bata rahey they : ''kal Insha-Allah yahan falan qatl hoga, aur kal Insha-Allah yahan falan qatl hoga.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jis jis jagah ki nishan dahi farmaee thi is mein zara bhi farq nahin aaya tha (wo wahin wahin qatl huey they) raawi bayan kartey hain, un sab ko eik doosrey par kunwen mein dal diya gaya phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''aey falan bin falan ! aey falan bin falan ! Allah aur uskey Rasool ne tum se jo wada farmaya tha kya tum ne usey sachcha paya, kyonkey Allah ne mujh se jo wada farmaya tha maine to usey sachcha paya hai?'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap be-rooh jismon se kaisey kalam farma rahey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main un se jo keh raha hun wo usey tum se ziyada sun rahey hain lekin wo mujhey kisi chiz ka jawab nahin dey saktey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5939,"Hazrat Unaisa binte Zaid bin Arqam apney walid se riwayat karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zaid ki bimari mein unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari bimari khatarnak nahin, lekin tumhari us waqt kya haalat hogi jab merey baad tumhari umr daraz hogi aur tum andhey ho jaaogey?'' unhoney arz kiya : main sawab ki ummid rakhtey huey sabr karunga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tab tum baghair hisab jannat mein dakhil ho jaaogey.'' rawiya bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ke baad wo na-bina ho gaey phir Allah ne unhen basaarat ata farmaee aur phir unhoney wafat paae. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
5940,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne merey zimmey aisi baat lagai jo maine na kahi ho to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' aur aapney ye isliye farmaya ke aapney kisi aadmi ko (kahin) bheja to usney aap par jhoot bola to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye badduaa farmaee, usey murda paya gaya, uska pet chaak ho chuka tha aur zamin ne usey qubul nahin kiya. dono hadison ko Imam Behaqi ne dalaeelun nubuwa mein riwayat kiya hai.  rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa."
5941,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khana talab kiya, aapney usey eik wasq jau diye , wo aadmi , uski biwi aur unka mehman us se khatey rahey lekin jab us shakhs ne wo naap liye to wo khatam ho gaey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum usey na naaptey to tum us se khatey rehtey aur wo tumharey liye hamesha rehta.'' rawahu Muslim."
5942,"Hazrat Aasim bin Kulaib apney walid se aur wo ansaar mein se eik aadmi se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham eik janaze mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareek huey to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik qabr par gorkan (qabr khodne wale) ko hidayaat detey huey suna : ''uskey paaon ki janib se khuli karo, uskey sar ki janib se khuli karo.'' jab aap wapis aaye to us (maiyat) ki aurat ki taraf se dawat ka pegham deney wala aap ko mila to aapney dawat qubul farmaee aur ham bhi aap ke sath they, khana pesh kiya gaya to aapney apna haath badhaya, phir logon ne (haath) badhaya, unhoney khana khaya, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney apney munh mein luqma chabatey huey farmaya : ''main eik aisi bakri ka gosht paata hun jo apney maalik ki ijazat ke baghair hasil ki gaee hai.'' us aurat ne apney wazaahati pegham mein arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine naqeea' ki taraf , jo ke bakriyon ki kharid aur farokht ka markaz hai, aadmi bheja tha ta ke wo merey liye eik bakri kharid laye, lekin wahan na mili to maine apney padosi ki taraf bheja, usney eik bakri khareedi hui thi, ke wo uski qeemat ke iwaz usey meri taraf bhej dey, lekin wo (padosi) na mila to maine us aurat ki taraf pegham bheja to usney usey meri taraf bhej diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye khana qaidiyon ko khila do.'' (rawahu Abu-Dawood aur al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
5943,"Hazrat Hizam bin Hisham apney walid sey, wo apney dada Habish bin Khalid , jo ke Umme-Ma'bad ke bhai hain, se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab Makka se nikala gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka se Madina ki taraf Muhajir ki haisiyat se rawana huey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Abu-Bakar aur Abu-Bakar ke azad karda ghulam Ammar bin Fuhaira they aur unki raahnumai karney waley Abdullah Laisi they, wo Umme-Ma'bad ke do khemon ke paas se guzrey to unhoney us se gosht aur khajoor ke mutalliq puchha ta ke wo us se kharid lein. lekin unhen uskey yahaan koi chiz na mili, jabkey unke paas zaade-rah nahin tha aur wo qehat saali ka shikar ho chukey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khemey ke eik koney main eik bakri dekhi to farmaya : ''Umme-Maabad! ye bakri kaisi hai?'' usney bataya ke ye laaghar pan ki wajeh se rewad ke sath nahin ja sakti, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya ye doodh deti hai?'' usney arz kya : ye is laaiq nahin hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mujhey ijazat deti ho ke main uska doodh dho lun?'' usney arz kiya, merey waliden qurban hon, agar aap is mein doodh dekhtey hain to zarur dho lein, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isey talab farmaya , uskey than ko apna daste-mubarak lagaya, Allah Taala ka naam liya, Umme-Ma'bad ke liye us bakri ke barey mein duaaey khair farmaey, usney paaon khol diye, doodh chhod diya, aur wo jugaali karney lagi , aapney eik bartan mangaaya jo eik jamaat ko aasooda kar sakta tha, is mein doodh doha aur itna doha ke is par jhaag aa gaya, phir aapney Umme-Ma'bad ko pilaya yahan tak ke wo khub sairab ho gayi, phir apney sathiyon ko pilaya yahan tak ke wo sairab ho gaey, phir aapney un sab ke aakhir par khud piya , phir aapney us bartan mein dusri martaba doodh doha yahan tak ke bartan bhar gaya, us (doodh) ko Umme- Maabad ke paas chhod diya, phir aapney us se Islam par baiat li phir sab uskey paas se kooch kar gaey. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah). Sharahus-sunnah, ibn Abdul-Bar ne al-isteea'ab mein aur ibne-Jozi ne isey kitabul-wafa mein riwayat kiya hai, aur hadees mein taweel qissa hai."
5944,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Usaid bin Huzair aur Ubada bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) apney kisi masle ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se guftgu kartey rahey yahan tak ke bahut zyada andheri raat mein raat ka kafi hissey guzar gaya, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se wapsi ke liye rawana huye, her eik ke haath mein chhoti si lathi thi, chunanche un dono mein se eik ki lathi ne roshni paida kar di yahan tak ke wo uski roshni mein chalney lagey , lekin jab un dono ki raahen alag alag huin to doosrey ke liye uski lathi ne roshni paida kar di, dono mein her eik apni lathi ki roshni mein chalney laga yahan tak ke wo apney ghar pahunch gaya. Bukhari."
5945,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ghazwae uhad ka waqt aaya to raat ke waqt merey walid ne mujhey bulaya aur kaha : main apney mutalliq samajhta hun ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mein se sab se pehley main Shahid hunga, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaat Mubarak ke ilawa main apney baad tujh se ziyada aziz shakhs koi nahin chhod kar ja raha, merey zimmey kuchh qarz hai usey ada karna aur apni behnon ke sath achchha suluk karna, subah hui to wo pehley Shahid they, maine unhen eik doosrey shakhs ke sath eik qabr mein dafn kiya. Bukhari."
5946,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke suffa ke saathi mohtaj log they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas do aadmiyon ka khana ho to wo teesrey ko sath ley jaey, jis shakhs ke paas chaar afrad ka khana ho to wo paanchwen ko ya chhatey ko sath ley jaey.'' aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) teen ko sath lekar aaye , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) das ko sath lekar gaey, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sham ka khana Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan khaya , phir wahin thehar gaey yahan tak ke Namaze-Isha padh li gaee , phir wapis tashrif ley aaye aur wahin thehar gaey yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khana khaya, phir jitna Allah ne chaha raat ka hissa guzar gaya to wo wapis apney ghar chaley gaey, unki ehliya (biwi) ne un se kaha : aap ko aap ke mehmano ke sath aaney se kis ne roka tha? unhoney puchha : kya tum ne unhen khana nahin khilaya? unhoney arz kiya : unhoney inkar kar diya yahan tak ke aap tashrif ley ayen, wo naraz ho gaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! main bilkul khana nahin khaaunga. aurat ne bhi qism kha li ke wo isey nahin khayegi aur mehmano ne bhi qism utha li ke wo bhi khana nahin khaeygey. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye (half uthana) shetan ki taraf se tha. unhoney khana mangaayaa, khud khaya aur unke sath mehmano ne bhi khaya , wo luqma uthatey to uskey nichey se aur ziyada ho jata tha, unhoney apni ehliya se farmaya : bano faraas ki behan ! ye kya maamla hai? unhoney kaha : meri aakhon ki thandak ki qism ! ye ab pehley se bhi teen guna ziyada hai. chunanche unhoney khaya aur isey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhi bheja , bayan kiya gaya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is mein se khaya (khaya). muttafaq aleh. aur Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ( کُنَّا نَسْمَعُ تَسْبِیْحَ الطَّعَامِ ( (baabul majuzaat) mein guzar chuki hai."
5947,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Najashi faut huey to ham baham (aapas mein) guftgu kartey they ke unki qabr par musalsal roshni nazar aa rahi hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5948,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghusl deney ka irada kiya to unhoney kaha : malum nahin ke jis tarah ham apney faut honey waley deegar afrad ke (ba-waqt ghusl) kapdey utaar detey they isi tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bhi kapdey utaar den ya ham kapdon samet ghusl den, jab unhoney ikhtilaf kiya to Allah ne un par neend taari kar di yahan tak ke un mein se her shakhs ki thodi uskey seeney ke sath lagney lagi. phir ghar ke eik koney se kisi ne un se baat ki magar Sahaba ko uskey barey mein kuchh malum nahin ke wo kon tha, (us ne kaha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kapdon samet ghusl do, wo khadey huey aur aap ko is tarah ghusl diya ke aap ki qamis aap par thi, wo qamis ke ooper pani girate they aur aap ki qamis ke sath maltey they. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
5949,"Hazrat ibne Mankadr se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke azad karda ghulam Safina (Raziallahu anhu) sarzameene Rome mein lashkar se bichhad gaey, ya unhen qaid kar liya gaya, wo lashkar ki talash mein daudney lagey to achcha sher se samna ho gaya, unhoney farmaya : Abu-Al-Haaris (Sher ki kunniyat) ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka azad karda ghulam hun, merey sath ye ye masla bana hai, sher dam hilaataa hua aap ke samney aaya, yahan tak ke wo aap ke pehlu mein khada ho gaya, jab wo kahin se (khofnak) aawaz sunta to wo uski taraf mutawajjeh ho jata, phir wo unki taraf aa jata yahan tak ke wo lashkar ke sath ja miley phir sher wapis chala gaya. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5950,"Hazrat Abu Jauzaa bayan kartey hain, Madina waley shadeed qehat (sukhe) ka shikar ho gaey to unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz kiya to unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr ki taraf dekho (jaao) aur is mein se aasman ki taraf kuchh surakh bana do yahan tak ke un par koi parda na ho, unhoney aisey hi kiya to un par khub barish hui yahan tak ke ghaas ug aai oont is qadr farba ho gaey ke wo charbi se phool gaey aur is saal ka naam aamul fataq yani (khushhali ka saal) rakha gaya. rawahu Darmi."
5951,"Hazrat Saeed bin Abdul Azeez bayan kartey hain, jab Harra ka waqia hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid mein teen roz tak Azan hui na Namaz aur na hi Saeed bin Musaiyeb masjid se bahar nikal sakey , unhen Namaz ka waqt , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr Mubarak se aaney wali mubham si aawaz se malum hota tha. rawahu Darmi."
5952,"Hazrat Abu Khulda bayan kartey hain, maine Abu Aaliya se kaha, kya Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadise suni hain? unhoney kaha : unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki das saal khidmat ki hai aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke haq mein dua farmaee jiski wajeh se unka baagh saal mein do martaba phal diya karta tha, aur is mein kastoori jaisi khushbu aati thi. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5953,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber se riwayat hai ke Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nafeel se mutalliq Arwa binte Aus ne Marwan bin Hakam ki adaalat mein muqadma pesh kiya aur daawa kiya ke unhoney meri kuchh zamin hasil kar li hai, Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : kya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees sun leney ke baad bhi unki zamin ke kuchh hisse par qabza karunga? Marwan ne kaha : tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kya suna hai? unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' jisney baalisht bhar zamin nahaq hasil ki to usey saton zaminon ka toq pehnaya jaeyga.'' tab Marwan ne kaha : iskey baad main aap se koi sabut nahin maangta . Saeed ne dua farmaee : aey Allah ! agar wo jhooti hai to usey andhi bana dey aur usey uski zamin mein maut dey. raawi bayan kartey hain, jab wo faut hui to wo andhi ho chuki thi aur wo apni zamin mein chal rahi thi ke eik gadhey mein giri aur faut ho gaee. aur Sahih Muslim mein Muhammad bin Zaid bin Abdullah bin umr se uskey ham-maani riwayat hai ke unhoney usey beenai se mehroom deewaron ko tatoltey huey dekha, aur wo kehti thi : mujhey Saeed ki badduaa lag gaee aur wo ghar ke us kunwen ke paas se guzri jiskey mutalliq usney un (Saeed (Raziallahu anhu)) se muqadma kiya tha, wo is mein giri aur wohi uski qabr bani. muttafaq aleh."
5954,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik lashkar rawana kiya, aur Saariya naami shakhs ko uska ameer muqarrar kiya, is beech mein ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) khutba irshad farma rahey they ke aap zor se kehney lagey : Saariya ! pahad ki taraf , phir lashkar ki taraf se eik qaasid aaya to usney kaha : Ameer ul mominin ! hamara dushman se muqabla hua to usney hamein shikast se dochaar kar diya tha magar achcha kisi ne zor se aawaz di : Saarya ! pahad ko na chhodo. ham ne apni pushtein pahad ki janib kar lein to Allah Taala ne unhen shikast se dochaar kar diya. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
5955,"Hazrat Nubaih bin Wahab se riwayat hai ke Kab , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaey, ehle majlis ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tazkira kiya, to Kab ne farmaya : her roz sattar hazar farishtey nazil hotey hain aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr Mubarak ko gher letey hain, wo apney par phad phadaatey hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood bhejtey hain, jab Sham hoti hai to wo ooper chadh jatey hain, aur itney hi farishtey aur utar aatey hain aur wo bhi isi tarah kartey hain, yahan tak ke jab (roze-qiyamat) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni qabr Mubarak se niklengey to aap sattar hazar farishton ke sath mein hongey wo aap ko lekar jaldi bhagengey. rawahu Darmi."
5956,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) mein se sab se pehley hamarey paas Musab bin Umer aur ibn Umme- Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye, unhoney hamein Quran padhaanaa shuru kiya, phir Ammar , Bilal aur Saad (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , phir umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bees Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tashrif laye, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye. maine Madina walon ko kisi chiz par itna khush nahin dekha jitna maine unhen aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aamad par khush dekha, yahan tak ke maine chhoti chhoti bachchiyon aur bachchon ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif la chukey hain, jab aap tashrif laye to main Sura Aala ke sath mufassal (tafseeli) Suraton mein se kaee suraten padh chuka tha. Bukhari."
5957,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma huey aur farmaya : ''Allah ne apney eik bandey ko ikhtiyar diya ke wo duniya ki nematon mein se jo chahey apney liye pasand kar ley ya phir wo us chiz ko ikhtiyar kar ley jo Allah Taala ke paas hai.'' (ye sun kar) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey, aur arz kiya : hamarey waliden aap par fidaa hon ! hamein unki is haalat par tajjub hua, logon ne kaha is buzurg ko dekho , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bandey ke mutalliq bata rahey hain ke Allah ne usey ikhtiyar diya hai ke wo duniya ki nematen pasand kar ley ya us chiz ko pasand kar ley jo uskey paas hai, aur wo keh raha hai hamarey waliden aap par fidaa hon. chunanche jis bandey ko ikhtiyar diya gaya tha wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi they, aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ham sab se ziyada is baat ko janney waley they. muttafaq aleh."
5958,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aath saal baad shohdaaey uhad par aisey Namaze janaza ada ki jaisey aap zindon aur faut shuda logon se rukhsat ho rahey hon, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''main tum se aagey aagey hun, main tum par gawah rahunga , mujh se tumhari mulaqat hoz par hogi, main usey dekh raha hun halanke main apni is jagah par hun, aur mujhey zamin ke khazanon ki chabiyan ata ki gaee hain, mujhey tumharey mutalliq ye khadsha (dar) nahin ke tum merey baad shirk karogey, lekin mujhey tumharey mutalliq duniya ka khadsha hai ke tum uskey mutalliq baham (aapas mein) sabqat ley janey ki koshish karogey.'' aur baaz raawiyon ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''tum baham (aapas mein) lado gey aur tum bhi isi tarah halak ho jaaogey jis tarah tum se pehley log halak huey they.'' muttafaq aleh."
5959,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Allah ke inaamat mein se ye bhi mujh par inaam hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey ghar mein aur meri baari mein wafat pai us waqt aap merey seeney se tek lagaey huey they, aur Allah ne aap ki wafat ke waqt merey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke luaab ko eik sath jama kar diya, (wo is tarah ke) Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas aaye to unke haath mein miswak thi, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh se tek lagaey huey they, maine dekha ke aap usey dekh rahey hain, maine pehchan liya ke aap miswak pasand kartey hain, maine arz kiya, main usey aap ke liye ley lun, aapney apney sar se ishara farmaya ke haan, maine usey hasil kiya, lekin aap ke liye usey chabaanaa mushkil tha, maine arz kya : kya main isey aap ki khatir naram kar dun? aapney apney sar Mubarak se ishara farmaya ke haan, maine isey naram kar diya, aur aap ke samney chamdey ka eik bartan tha jis mein pani tha, aap apney haath pani mein dakhil farmatey aur unhen apney chehrey par phertey aur farmatey : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, maut ki sakhtiyan hoti hain.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna daste Mubarak uthaya aur farmaney lagey : (aey Allah !) aalaa saath nasib farma.'' yahan tak ke aap ki rooh qabz ho gaee aur aap ka daste Mubarak jhuk gaya. Bukhari."
5960,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo Nabi (maut ke marz mein) bimar hota hai to usey duniya aur aakhirat ke beech ikhtiyar diya jata hai.'' aur jis marz mein aap ki rooh qabz ki gaee , us marz mein aap par hichki ka sakht hamla hua tha, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''un logon ke sath jin par tu ney inaam farmaya, Anbiya (Alaihissalam), siddiqeen, shuhda aur sualeheen (ke sath).'' maine jaan liya ke aap ko ikhtiyar diya gaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
5961,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka marz shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaya to aap par karb (baichaini) aur takleef chhaaney lagi , to Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, abba jaan ko kitni takleef hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''aaj ke baad aap ke abba jaan ko koi takleef nahin hogi.'' jab aap wafat pa gaey to Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : abba jaan ! aapney apney rab ke bulaawey par labbaik kaha, abba jaan ! aap, jin ka thikana Jannattul Firdaus hai, abba jaan ! ham Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko aap ki maut ki khabar sunatey hain, jab aap ko dafn kar diya gaya to Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Anas ! tumharey dil Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par mitti dalney ke liye kaisey aamada ho gaey? Bukhari."
5962,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to habshiyon ne aap ki aamad ki khushi par apney nezon ka khel pesh kiya. aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : maine us roz sey, jis roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye, ziyada Husain aur ziyada roshan koi din nahin dekha, aur maine us din sey, jis din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai , ziyada qabeeh aur ziyada taareek koi aur din nahin dekha. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : farmaya : jis roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madiney mein dakhil huey they to us se her chiz roshan ho gaee thi, chunanche jis din aapney wafat pai thi us se her chiz taareek ho gaee thi, ham ne apney haath mitti se saaf nahin kiye they aur abhi ham aap ki tadfeen mein masroof they ke ham ne apney dilon ko ajnabi paya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi aur Tirmizi ."
5963,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki rooh qabz ki gaee to aap ki tadfeen ke mutalliq Sahaba mein ikhtilaf paida ho gaya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se (is barey mein) kuchh suna hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah Nabi ki rooh usi jagah qabz farmata hai jahan wo pasand farmata hai ke uski tadfeen ho. ''tum aap ko aap ke bistar ki jagah par dafn karo. rawahu Tirmizi."
5964,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haalate sehat mein farmaya kartey they : ''kisi Nabi ki rooh us waqt tak qabz nahin ki jati jab tak unhen unka jannati thikana nahin dikha diya jata hai, phir unhen ikhtiyar diya jata hai.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab aap par maut taari hui us waqt aap ka sar Mubarak meri raan par tha, aap par be hoshi taari hui, phir ifaaqa (fayda) hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni nazar chhat ki taraf uthai , phir farmaya : ''aey Allah ! aalaa sath nasib farma , maine kaha : tab to aap hamein ikhtiyar nahin karengey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain maine jaan liya ke wo hadees jo aap hamein bayan kiya kartey they. jabke aap sehat mand they : ''kisi Nabi ki rooh qabz nahin ki jati yahan tak ke wo apna jannati thikana dekh leta hai, phir usey ikhtiyar diya jata hai.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo aakhiri baat farmaee wo ye thi : ''aey Allah ! aalaa sath nasib farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
5965,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney marze wafat mein farma rahey they : ''Aaisha ! maine jo khana khaibar ke moqe par khaya tha uski takleef musalsal uthata raha hun, aur ye wo waqt aa gaya hai ke aisa malum hota hai ke us zahar ki wajeh se meri sheh rag kat jaeygi.'' Bukhari."
5966,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par maut ke marz ke aasaar zahir honey lagey, to us waqt (aap ke) ghar mein kuchh afrad they un mein umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''laao main tumhen eik tehreer likh dun jiskey baad tum kabhi gumrah na hongey.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aap par takleef ka ghalba hai aur tumharey paas Quran hai, tumharey liye Allah ki kitab kafi hai, is par ghar mein mojud afrad mein ikhtilaf pad gaya, aur wo jhagad padey, koi keh raha tha, laao, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen likh den, aur koi wohi keh raha tha jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha, chunanche jab shor aur ghul aur ikhtilaf ziyada ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas se uth jaao.'' Ubaidullah ne bayan kiya, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : sab se badi musibat ye thi ke unka ikhtilaf aur shor aur shaghab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki tehreer ke darmiyan haael (rukawat) ho gaya. aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Abi Muslim Al Ahwal ki riwayat mein hai, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Jumerat ke din ka zikr kiya, aur Jumerat ke din kya hua? phir wo roney lagey , itna roey ke unke aansuon ne sangrezon ko tar kar diya. maine kaha : ibne-Abbas ! Jumerat ke din kya hua? unhoney farmaya is roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki takleef shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaee, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey shaaney ki haddi do main tumhen tehreer likh dun, uskey baad tum kabhi gumrah na hogey.'' unhoney ikhtilaf kar liya, halanke Nabi ke yahan tanaaza' munasib nahin, unhoney kaha : unki kya haalat hai? kya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (marz ki wajeh sey) aisi baat farma rahey hain, unhen samajhney ki koshish karo, phir wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bar-bar poochhney ki koshish kartey rahey lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey chhod do, mujhey merey haal par rehney do main jis haalat mein hun wo us sey, jis ke liye tum keh rahey ho, behtar hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen teen baaton ki wasiyat farmaee : '' mushrekin ko jazeera Arab se nikal dena, wufood ko isi tarah atiyaat detey rehna jis tarah main unhen atiyaat diya karta tha.'' aur raawi ne teesri baat nahin ki ya uskey mutalliq unhoney kaha : main usey bhool gaya hun, Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ye (kehna ke unhoney teesri baat bayan nahin ki) Suleman (Alaihissalam) ka qol hai. muttafaq aleh."
5967,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Umme-Aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chalen unki ziyaarat karen jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki ziyaarat kiya kartey they, jab ham unke paas pahunchey to wo roney lagin, un dono hazraat ne unhen kaha : aap kyon roti hain, kya aap ko malum nahin ke Allah ke yahan jo hai wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye behtar hai? unhoney farmaya : main isliye nahin ro rahi ke mujhey ilm nahin ke Allah Taala ke yahan jo hai wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye behtar hai, main to isliye ro rahi hun ke aasman se wahi ka aana munqata' (khatm) ho chuka hai, Umme-Aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono hazraat ko bhi roney par aamada kar diya, wo bhi unke sath ronaa shuru ho gaey. rawahu Muslim."
5968,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney marze wafat mein (apney hujrey sey) bahar tashrif laye, ham us waqt masjid mein they, aapney apney sar par patti baandh rakhi thi, aap member ki taraf badhey aur is par jalwa afroz huye, ham bhi aap ke qarib huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main apni is jagah se hoz (kausar) ko dekh raha hun.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik bandey par duniya aur uski zeb aur zeenat pesh ki gaee lekin usney aakhirat ko pasand kiya. '' raawi bayan kartey hain sirf Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hi is baat ko samajh sakey , unki aakhon se aansu bahney lagey aur aap zaaro qatar roney lagey , phir arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! nahin, balke ham aap par apney waliden , apni janen aur apney amwaal qurban kar dengey, raawi bayan kartey hain, phir aap member se nichey tashrif laye, phir wafat tak dobara member par jalwa afroz nahin huey. rawahu Darmi."
5969,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Sura-Nasar nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur farmaya : ''mujhey meri wafat ki ittilaa di gaee hai.'' wo roney lagin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mat ro'ein, kyonkey merey ehle khana mein se sab se pehley aap mujhey milengi.'' is par wo hans den. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi zauja (biwi) mohtarma ne unhen dekh liya to unhoney kaha : Fatima ! ham ne aap ko rotey huey dekha phir aap ko hanstey huey dekha, (kya maamla tha?) unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bataya ke mujhey meri wafat ki ittilaa di gaee hai to is par main roney lagi , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''aap mat ro'ein, kyonkey merey ehle khana mein se sab se pehley aap mujhey milengi.'' to is par main hans di. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ki nusrat aur Fateh aa gaee.'' aur ehle Yamen aaye , wo naram dil hain, aur eman yamni hai aur hikmat yamni hai.'' sanad rawahu Darmi."
5970,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : haaye sar phata ja raha hai (aur unhoney maut ki taraf ishara kiya) tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar aisi surat hui (tumhari maut waqey ho gaee) aur main zinda hua to main tumharey liye maghfirat talab karunga aur tumharey liye dua karunga.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : afsos ! Allah ki qism ! main aap ke mutalliq ye khayal karti hun ke aap meri maut pasand farmatey hain, agar aisey ho gaya to aap agley hi roz kisi dusri aurat se shaadi kar lengey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke main apney sar phatney ka izhar karta hun, maine irada kiya tha ke main Abu-Bakar aur unke bete ko bula bhejun aur un (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ko khalifa naamzad kar dun, taake koi daawa karney wala uska daawa na karey ya koi khahish rakhney wala uski khahish na rakhey , phir maine kaha : Allah khud hi (kisi aur ki khilaafat ka ( inkar farma dega aur momin (kisi aur ko khilaafat sey) door kar dengey. ya Allah (kisi aur ki khilaafat) hata dega aur momin inkar kar dengey.'' Bukhari."
5971,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) janaazey se farigh ho kar Baqee se wapis merey paas tashrif laye aur aapney mujhey is haal mein paya ke merey sar mein dard tha, aur main keh rahi thi : haaye dard ki wajeh se sar phata ja raha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin balke Aaisha ! main, aur mera sar dard se phata ja raha hai.'' farmaya : ''agar tum mujh se pehley wafat pa gaeen to ye tumharey liye Muzar (nuksandeh) nahin kyonkey is surat mein , main tumhen ghusl dunga, tujhey kafan pahnaoonga , tumhari Namaze janaza padhunga aur tumhen dafn karunga.'' maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! aap ke mutalliq mera bhi yehi khayal hai, agar aapney is tarah (ghusl, kafan aur dafn waghera) kiya to aap merey ghar wapis aaeyngey, wahan apni kisi biwi se sohbat karengey, (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye, phir aap ko takleef zahir hui jis mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai. rawahu Darmi."
5972,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Quraish mein se eik aadmi unke walid Ali bin Husain ke paas aaya aur usney kaha : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees na sunaun? unhoney farmaya : haan, Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees hamein sunaao, us aadmi ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar huey to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aap ke paas aaye to unhoney kaha : Muhammad ! Allah ne aap ki takrim (izzat) aur tazeem ki khatir mujhey aap ki taraf bheja hai, wo aap ke liye khas hai, wo aap se us chiz ke mutalliq daryaft karta hai, jiskey mutalliq wo aap se behtar janta hai, wo farmata hai : aap apney aap ko kaisa mehsus kartey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael ! main apney aap ko maghmum (gham mein) paata hun, aur Jibrael ! main apney aap ko karb (baichaini) mein mehsus karta hun.'' phir wo doosrey roz aaye to unhoney aap se yehi kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wohi jawab diya jo aapney pehley roz diya tha. phir wo teesrey roz aap ke paas aaye to unhoney aap se wohi kuchh kaha jo pehley roz kaha tha, aur aapney bhi unhen wohi jawab diya, aur aakhiri baar Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ke sath Ismail naami farishta aaya jo eik lakh farishton ka sardar hai, aur uska her matehet farishta lakh farishton ka sardar hai, usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) se us (farishten) ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne arz kiya : ye maut ka farishta hai, wo aap ke paas aaney ki ijazat talab kar raha hai, usney aap se pehley kisi aadmi se ijazat talab ki hai na aap ke baad kisi aadmi se ijazat talab karega. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey ijazat dey den.'' usey ijazat de-di gaee, usney salam kiya, phir kaha : Muhammad ! Allah ne mujhey aap ki taraf bheja hai, agar aap apni rooh qabz karney ki mujhey ijazat den to main qabz kar lunga, aur agar aapney ijazat na farmaee to main usey qabz nahin karunga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maut ke farishtey ! kya tum aisey karogey?'' usney kaha : haan , kyonkey mujhey ye hukm diya gaya hai ke main aap ki chaahat ka ehtiraam karun, raawi bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ki taraf dekha to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Muhammad ! Allah aap ki mulaqat ka mushtaaq hai, tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne malakul-maut se farmaya : ''tumhen jo hukm diya gaya hai uski taameel karo.'' usney aap ki rooh qabz ki, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai aur ta'ziyat karney waley hazir huey to unhoney ghar ke koney se aawaz suni : ehle bait ! tum par salamti ho, Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkat hon, be-shak Allah ki kitab mein her musibat se taziyat aur tasalli hai, her halak honey wali chiz ka moawza hai, aur her nuqsan ka tadaaruk (bharpaai) hai, Allah ki tofiq ke sath Allah se daro , sirf us se ummid wabasta karo, khasaray wala shakhs wo hai jo sawab se mehroom ho gaya Ali (Zainul Aabideen(Reh.)) ne kaha : kya tum jantey ho ke wo shakhs kon tha? wo khizr (Alaihissalam) they. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi dalaeelun nubuwa)."
5973,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (tarka mein) koi Dinar chhoda na dirham , koi bakri chhodi na oont aur na hi kisi chiz ki wasiyat ki. rawahu Muslim."
5974,"Hazrat Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhai Amr bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni wafat ke waqt koi Dinar chhoda na dirham , koi ghulam chhoda na londi , aapney apna safed khachar , apna aslaha aur kuchh zamin chhodi thi, aur us (zameen) ko bhi sadqa qarar dey diya tha. Bukhari."
5975,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri wirasat Dinar ki surat mein taqseem nahin hogi, maine apni paak biviyon ke kharchey aur aamilon ki zarooriyaat ke ikhrajat ke baad jo chhoda hai wo sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5976,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamari virasat nahin hoti, hamara tarka sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5977,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ummat ke afrad par rehmat ka irada farmata hai to us (ummat) se pehley uskey Nabi ki rooh qabz farma leta hai, aur wo us (nabi) ko us (ummat) ke liye uskey aagey meer manzil aur pesh-rau (leader) bana deta hai, aur jab wo kisi ummat ki halakat ka irada farmata hai to Nabi ki zindagi mein us (ummat) par azab nazil farma kar usko halak kar deta hai aur wo (nabi) unki halakat ke manzar ka mushaahida karkey us se apni aankhen thandi karta hai kyonkey unhoney uski takzeeb (jhutlaaya) ki hoti hai aur uskey hukm ki nafarmani ki hoti hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5978,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! tum mein se kisi par eik din aisa bhi aaeyga ke wo mujhey nahin dekhega, phir agar wo mujhey dekh ley to ye usey apney ehal aur ayaal aur apney maal ke milney se bhi ziyada pasandida hoga.'' rawahu Muslim."
